43
00:06:15,775 --> 00:06:16,901
What?

44
00:06:21,948 --> 00:06:24,917
l'm the Saamy who gave ''laddu''
to Tirupathi Saamy (God).

45
00:06:25,284 --> 00:06:28,412
''Halwa'' of this Theft shop,
Old woman of ''ldli'' shop.

46
00:06:28,621 --> 00:06:31,749
lf you hear the noise of batons...
lt's Saamy!

47
00:06:32,125 --> 00:06:35,253
Lord Nellaiapparsaamy will
secure us like a fence.

48
00:06:35,461 --> 00:06:38,760
l'll be a fence,
if you come to me.

49
00:06:38,965 --> 00:06:42,025
Lord Kanthimathi saamy will
fulfill your wishes.

50
00:06:42,301 --> 00:06:45,600
l'll come to you & fulfill
your wishes.

