l had seen MGR's films sitting on
sand at a touring talkies.

64
00:09:08,114 --> 00:09:14,747
l'm master of my own destiny.

65
00:09:14,954 --> 00:09:18,253
l spent my days sleeping in
lorry sheds of Uthukottai.

66
00:09:18,457 --> 00:09:21,756
l'm an expert in breaking
bones with a baton.

67
00:09:21,961 --> 00:09:24,759
Butter of Utthukuli.
Jaggery of Tiruchendur.

68
00:09:24,964 --> 00:09:28,593
What's there in Chennai?
Not a drop of water.

69
00:09:28,801 --> 00:09:31,929
Test the waters before entering into it.

70
00:09:32,138 --> 00:09:35,437
Tell me if there's any one
to challenge me.

71
00:09:35,641 --> 00:09:38,769
You'll get a kick, if you
take ''Tuticorin Salt''.

72
00:09:38,978 --> 00:09:42,277
l'm the famed Dindugul lock.
What l'm saying is right.

73
00:10:15,848 --> 00:10:28,784
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

74
00:10:29,195 --> 00:10:31,322
Hey! Why are you creating
trouble here?

75
00:10:32,031 --> 00:10:34,499
He has beaten me!

76
00:10:37,203 --> 00:10:38,431
Hey!...How dare you touch me?

77
00:10:41,374 --> 00:10:46,175
lf a man gets drunk & creates
trouble in my station limits,

78
00:10:46,379 --> 00:10:47,505
Won't l hold him by his neck?

79
00:10:47,713 --> 00:10:49,237
l'll beat you.

80
00:10:49,882 --> 00:10:52,248
You're under arrest!
- Do you've a warrant?

81
00:10:52,885 --> 00:10:56,844
Will this Punctuality Paramasivam
come without a warrant?

82
00:10:57,056 --> 00:10:59,024
Take it man! Read it.

83
00:10:59,892 --> 00:11:05,194
Sir, please come to station with me.
Your's `Punctuality Paramasivam'.

84
00:11:09,602 --> 00:11:10,864
What's this? - Under arrest.

85
00:11:11,070 --> 00:11:12,264
`Upper' arrest is enough for you.

86
00:11:13,739 --> 00:11:14,865
Throwing bottles!

87
00:11:15,074 --> 00:11:16,541
Did you see how perfectly
l found out?

88
00:11:16,742 --> 00:11:17,606
Statesmanship!

89
00:11:18,411 --> 00:11:19,810
One must have intelligence first.

90
00:11:20,079 --> 00:11:21,876
Don't think l'm not
brave enough.

91
00:11:22,081 --> 00:11:23,878
ln a jiffy, l can break open
the gate & beat you.

92
00:11:24,083 --> 00:11:25,550
Why do you want to break?
lt's already open.

93
00:11:25,751 --> 00:11:28,219
Hey! Catch it...Catch it...
Couldn't you tell me it isn't locked?

94
00:11:30,256 --> 00:11:32,884
Hey! Wait...he's having
the bail order.

95
00:11:33,092 --> 00:11:35,560
lt's against law, if we keep a man
in jail with a bail.

96
00:11:35,761 --> 00:11:38,059
Will you give me the bail and
come out of the jail?

97
00:11:39,098 --> 00:11:40,725
lf you write on a white paper,
it's warrant.

98
00:11:40,933 --> 00:11:42,730
lf Gandhi smiles on a green note,
is it a bail order?

99
00:11:43,102 --> 00:11:45,570
You're maintaining
law & order perfectly. - Sir bail!

100
00:11:47,606 --> 00:11:49,403
Sir, how can you release
after filing F.l.R?

101
00:11:49,608 --> 00:11:51,576
Put this man into the jail
instead of him.

102
00:11:51,777 --> 00:11:53,574
We can change people
but can we change names?

103
00:11:53,779 --> 00:11:55,076
What's this man's name?
- Kuppusaamy.

104
00:11:55,281 --> 00:11:56,578
That man's name?
- Saamy.

105
00:11:56,782 --> 00:11:57,578
Add `Kuppu' before Saamy's name.

106
00:11:57,783 --> 00:11:58,977
And put this `Kuppa' (trash)
into the jail.

107
00:12:00,119 --> 00:12:00,949
How did you manage it?

108
00:12:01,087 --> 00:12:02,554
You were arrested yesterday
but out today.

109
00:12:02,788 --> 00:12:03,584
lt's the power of money.

110
00:12:03,789 --> 00:12:05,916
Where can l get this `matter'?
- You mean `Marijuana'?

111
00:12:06,125 --> 00:12:07,922
lf you go to ''Rettai Marathadi''
and ask for 'sugar cane refuse'.

112
00:12:08,127 --> 00:12:08,593
You'll get it.

113
00:12:08,794 --> 00:12:10,591
'Sugar cane refuse'?
- That's the other name of Marijuana.

114
00:12:11,630 --> 00:12:13,757
Do you get girls here?

115
00:12:14,133 --> 00:12:17,762
Girls! MLA is running it as a wholesale
trade in Melapalayam.

116
00:12:17,970 --> 00:12:20,598
Ward & district level leaders are
doing it in retail in lodges.

117
00:12:20,806 --> 00:12:23,934
Not only that spurious liquor is
brewed behind the market.

118
00:12:24,310 --> 00:12:26,778
There are hired henchmen
in Palayamkottai.

119
00:12:26,979 --> 00:12:28,776
There are hired killers
in our area.

120
00:12:29,148 --> 00:12:31,673
Rowdies are spreading out to
4 states from our place only.

121
00:12:32,651 --> 00:12:35,449
Annachi Perumal Pitchai is the
king pin of this illegal trade.

122
00:12:35,821 --> 00:12:37,618
Why are you asking me
all the details?

123
00:12:37,990 --> 00:12:39,958
l never asked, you told me
everything yourself.

124
00:12:40,159 --> 00:12:42,354
Oh! ls this known as making
others sing?

125
00:12:49,335 --> 00:12:52,634
Hey! What's going on man?
Leave him...

126
00:12:52,838 --> 00:12:55,807
Hey what did he do?
- Sir, he stole my briefcase.

127
00:12:57,510 --> 00:13:00,479
How dare you steal a briefcase
in the middle of a busy town?

128
00:13:00,679 --> 00:13:01,236
Give it to me.

129
00:13:02,181 --> 00:13:03,808
Constable, put him into the jeep.

130
00:13:04,683 --> 00:13:05,809
Whose briefcase is this?

131
00:13:06,018 --> 00:13:07,315
Sir, it's mine, there are
Rs.3 lakhs cash in it.

132
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:11,650
Let it be there! Come to the station,
sign the papers and take it.

133
00:13:11,857 --> 00:13:13,154
Hey! Why are you gathering
around here? Go away.

134
00:13:25,704 --> 00:13:28,002
Sir greetings!
- Who's stopping the police jeep?

135
00:13:28,207 --> 00:13:30,835
lf police like you resort to stealing,
what do we thieves do then?

136
00:13:31,377 --> 00:13:32,173
Give me way.

137
00:13:32,378 --> 00:13:35,347
Brother, you can't go from here
without answering me.

138
00:13:35,548 --> 00:13:37,015
Hey! Run over the jeep on him.

139
00:15:18,150 --> 00:15:20,380
He said he's Saamy (God) but he's
beating like a devil.

140
00:16:22,047 --> 00:16:22,843
Give it man.

141
00:16:24,216 --> 00:16:26,013
Hey, stop it man!

142
00:16:26,719 --> 00:16:30,519
How dare a rowdy like you
beat a policeman?

143
00:16:30,723 --> 00:16:33,453
Am l a vandal and you a policeman?

144
00:16:34,727 --> 00:16:36,695
You're not a D.D. Dandapani
but KD(vandal) Dandapani.

145
00:16:37,229 --> 00:16:39,527
Looks like you'll give your uniform
to make him a policeman.

146
00:16:39,732 --> 00:16:42,530
He's a wastrel, you're supporting him.
Arrest him.

147
00:16:42,735 --> 00:16:44,703
l know whom l should arrest.
Who are you?

148
00:16:45,904 --> 00:16:50,534
One, two, three, four, five...

149
00:16:52,911 --> 00:16:54,003
l'm Aru(Six) Saamy.

150
00:16:54,246 --> 00:16:57,215
Deputy Commissioner of Police,
Tirunelveli city.

151
00:17:00,753 --> 00:17:03,881
Bloody rascal, you were stealing
spare parts in lorry sheds.

152
00:17:04,089 --> 00:17:05,716
And you're robbing people here?

153
00:17:06,425 --> 00:17:07,153
Arrest him.

154
00:17:22,608 --> 00:17:24,132
Did you salute me
or your big bellies?

155
00:17:24,276 --> 00:17:25,971
Once more... - Yes sir.

156
00:17:26,111 --> 00:17:28,579
He's taking us to task for salute.
Don't know what's in store.

157
00:17:29,448 --> 00:17:31,245
Who hoisted this flag?
- l did sir.

158
00:17:31,450 --> 00:17:32,576
You've hoisted it 3 inches lower!

159
00:17:32,785 --> 00:17:34,753
l couldn't see 3 inch difference
at the height of 30 feet.

160
00:17:34,953 --> 00:17:36,750
Then, you wouldn't be able to see a
thief 30 feet away from you.

161
00:17:36,955 --> 00:17:37,922
One week's suspension!

162
00:17:38,791 --> 00:17:40,588
Oh God! Then l think
l'll be dismissed.

163
00:17:40,793 --> 00:17:42,590
Do you know march past?
- They've forgotten all that.

164
00:17:42,795 --> 00:17:43,591
Poor guys!

165
00:17:43,796 --> 00:17:45,923
They've become like statutes
standing in one place for 20 years.

166
00:17:46,131 --> 00:17:47,928
But l'm not like them sir
if you say l'll achieve it.

167
00:17:48,133 --> 00:17:49,930
lf you say milk l'll become butter
if you say pulse l'll become sambar.

168
00:17:50,135 --> 00:17:51,102
lf l say fire, will you
immolate yourself?

169
00:17:51,303 --> 00:17:52,429
Will you kill if l
pay you money?

170
00:17:54,139 --> 00:17:55,936
Will you throw out Kuppa (trash) and
add `Kuppa' to Saamy's name.

171
00:17:56,308 --> 00:17:57,605
First zip up your pant.
- Yes sir.

172
00:17:57,810 --> 00:18:00,108
Look here! l'm telling
everyone.

173
00:18:00,479 --> 00:18:01,946
Go and get drunk any where.

174
00:18:02,147 --> 00:18:03,774
Wear shoes or not?
Cut hair or not?

175
00:18:03,982 --> 00:18:05,609
Wear uniform or not?
Wear your cap or not?

176
00:18:05,818 --> 00:18:07,115
l'm not bothered about all these.

177
00:18:07,486 --> 00:18:11,115
You must follow the orders strictly,
if anyone bungles or refuses.

178
00:18:11,490 --> 00:18:13,117
No warnings, suspensions or dismissals.

179
00:18:13,492 --> 00:18:15,790
l'll kill you overnight and throw
your bodies into river Thamaraparani.

180
00:18:15,994 --> 00:18:16,619
Mind it!

181
00:18:16,829 --> 00:18:18,956
100 Criminals might escape,
forget about them.

182
00:18:19,164 --> 00:18:20,791
But an innocent should
never be punished.

183
00:18:21,834 --> 00:18:23,631
A policeman must be proud.

184
00:18:24,002 --> 00:18:26,800
lf anyone disturbs peace in public places.
Bash him up right there.

185
00:18:27,172 --> 00:18:30,141
We must be a friend to people
and a rogue to rogues.

186
00:18:30,843 --> 00:18:33,641
We policemen should salute
only our National flag.

187
00:18:34,513 --> 00:18:35,810
lt's a town with a radius
of just 5 kms.

188
00:18:36,014 --> 00:18:37,311
Though so many policemen are here, still
crimes are being committed regularly.

189
00:18:37,516 --> 00:18:38,642
Who's responsible for it?

190
00:18:39,017 --> 00:18:40,143
Mr.Paramasivam! - Yes sir.

191
00:18:40,352 --> 00:18:41,649
Buses, lorries plying in Tirunelveli,

192
00:18:41,854 --> 00:18:42,980
Wine shops, jewellery shops,
provision shops,

193
00:18:43,188 --> 00:18:45,816
Lodges, hotels, colleges
businessmen, students,

194
00:18:46,191 --> 00:18:47,317
Government servants, lawyers, doctors,

195
00:18:47,526 --> 00:18:49,824
l want the entire list of people in
this town within 24 hours.

196
00:18:50,028 --> 00:18:50,653
Why do you want doctors list?

197
00:18:50,863 --> 00:18:52,660
l must know the number
of fake doctors.

198
00:18:53,132 --> 00:18:54,599
Unwanted lorries shouldn't
enter the town.

199
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:56,665
Buses shouldn't stop at
unnecessary places.

200
00:18:57,035 --> 00:18:59,162
No one should be in a petty shop
for more than 10 minutes.

201
00:18:59,371 --> 00:19:01,168
A group of 4 people shouldn't
walk on the roads.

202
00:19:01,540 --> 00:19:04,008
Most important, no one must tie their
lungies above their thighs.

203
00:19:04,209 --> 00:19:05,608
lf they refuse,
kick their butts.

204
00:19:05,811 --> 00:19:07,176
Sir, this is like MlSA rule.

205
00:19:07,546 --> 00:19:08,171
What is my name?

206
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:10,507
Read it from the end `SA' `Ml'! MlSA.

207
00:19:11,717 --> 00:19:14,515
l'm not a policeman but a rogue.

208
00:19:47,586 --> 00:19:48,382
Rascal!

209
00:19:49,021 --> 00:19:50,923
Unload it slowly,
don't hurt yourself.

210
00:19:50,923 --> 00:19:54,882
l'll supply mustard, pepper, cumin and
fenugreek in 50 & 100 gms pack.

211
00:19:55,093 --> 00:19:58,893
l'll supply sugar in 1 kg pack.
Take delivery tomorrow.

212
00:20:10,943 --> 00:20:12,843
Sir, Rs.4,500, last week's bill.

213
00:20:13,045 --> 00:20:16,071
Give it to my grand daughter as usual.

214
00:20:17,950 --> 00:20:19,247
Come here for a moment.

215
00:20:23,288 --> 00:20:24,915
Grandpa, did you call me?
- Yes.

216
00:20:25,123 --> 00:20:26,420
Take that money and keep it safely.

217
00:20:28,460 --> 00:20:32,089
Sugar bag appears very weak.
ls it not feeling well?

218
00:20:32,297 --> 00:20:34,094
What's the weight of this bag?
- 100 kgs.

219
00:20:34,299 --> 00:20:35,926
You bought it after
weighing it, didn't you?

220
00:20:36,134 --> 00:20:38,261
No, l must weigh it now.
- Weigh it & show me.

221
00:20:38,470 --> 00:20:39,937
Hey! Put the bag on weighing scale.

222
00:20:44,910 --> 00:20:47,538
lt's 94 kgs. only!
What happened to 6 kgs?

223
00:20:47,913 --> 00:20:51,610
ls it for this bag only or
is it a feature to all your bags?

224
00:20:52,150 --> 00:20:54,778
lf your proprietor comes to know,
you'll lose your job.

225
00:20:55,487 --> 00:20:58,285
We get 40 paise per packet
as commission.

226
00:20:58,490 --> 00:21:00,219
We are doing it to supplement
our meager earnings.

227
00:21:00,425 --> 00:21:02,290
You are making us lose money.
- Forgive me sir.

228
00:21:02,494 --> 00:21:03,119
l'll take leave mother

229
00:21:03,996 --> 00:21:05,122
Hereafter this mistake
will not be repeated.

230
00:21:05,330 --> 00:21:09,960
Your son is labour officer
for name's sake only.

231
00:21:10,335 --> 00:21:14,465
lf he takes bribe from shop owners
he'll easily make money.

232
00:21:14,673 --> 00:21:19,133
He's talking like a mad man
about honesty, sincerity.

233
00:21:19,344 --> 00:21:22,802
That's why we are struggling
to meet both ends meet.

234
00:21:23,015 --> 00:21:24,642
Grandpa, don't criticize dad.

235
00:21:25,017 --> 00:21:27,485
Desiring other's money is a sin.

236
00:21:27,853 --> 00:21:29,320
Money earned by hard work
only, will be with us.

237
00:21:29,855 --> 00:21:31,720
Mother, l've taken
Rs.100 for bus pass.

238
00:21:32,024 --> 00:21:33,787
Grandma, l'll go to college.
- Okay dear.

239
00:21:34,026 --> 00:21:34,822
Sister, l'll go.

240
00:21:35,127 --> 00:21:38,995
Meenakshi, your husband
is not to be seen all day?

241
00:21:39,264 --> 00:21:42,062
Yes, is your son-in-law behaving
like a brahmin?

242
00:21:42,267 --> 00:21:43,996
He went to conduct a sacrifice.

243
00:21:44,202 --> 00:21:46,329
Don't know where he might be
picking up trouble now?

244
00:21:52,210 --> 00:21:54,508
Stop, park your vehicle aside.
- Have you started it?

245
00:21:54,713 --> 00:21:55,680
l'm on my way to conduct
a ceremony.

246
00:21:55,881 --> 00:21:57,178
Let's take care of things
while coming back.

247
00:21:57,382 --> 00:21:59,612
Forget it, park it aside and
take out your documents.

248
00:21:59,818 --> 00:22:01,513
Documents mean?
- lnsurance.

249
00:22:01,887 --> 00:22:04,685
For me, you or my bike?
- Of the bike?

250
00:22:04,890 --> 00:22:06,118
Then, take it.

251
00:22:06,892 --> 00:22:08,860
R.C.book! - Take R.C book.

252
00:22:09,061 --> 00:22:11,689
Road tax! - There's no road but
you're asking for road tax.

253
00:22:12,497 --> 00:22:15,523
What's this you're riding the bike without
changing the number plate?

254
00:22:17,235 --> 00:22:18,031
Take it.

255
00:22:18,236 --> 00:22:19,362
Why are you showing
like channel V?

256
00:22:19,638 --> 00:22:22,539
You're changing rules at
the drop of a hat.

257
00:22:22,741 --> 00:22:25,369
So, l've a white, black and
yellow number plate.

258
00:22:25,577 --> 00:22:29,445
When you decide,
l'll fix that number plate.

259
00:22:29,648 --> 00:22:31,878
You can fix it later, take out
your license. - License?

260
00:22:33,085 --> 00:22:34,814
Take it...Check it.

261
00:22:36,254 --> 00:22:39,052
You're without the tuft
in this photo.

262
00:22:39,424 --> 00:22:41,051
That photo was taken
when l was a student.

263
00:22:41,259 --> 00:22:42,385
So, l didn't have a tuft then.

264
00:22:42,594 --> 00:22:46,155
lt is passport size photo,
infact l had gone there without pant.

265
00:22:46,365 --> 00:22:47,559
Do you need all that?

266
00:22:47,766 --> 00:22:50,394
How to make him pay fine?
Can you do an 8?

267
00:22:51,770 --> 00:22:53,328
Not that, on your bike
can you do it?

268
00:22:53,538 --> 00:22:55,904
Would they grant me a license
without doing that?

269
00:22:56,775 --> 00:22:59,243
Then, make a 7 on your bike
- 7?

270
00:23:00,445 --> 00:23:02,743
l think he's expecting some
bribe from me.

271
00:23:03,115 --> 00:23:05,583
Come & sit on my bike
l'll do a 7.5.

272
00:23:05,784 --> 00:23:10,187
How can you do that?
- Sit man, l'll show you.

273
00:23:10,389 --> 00:23:14,587
l'm sitting. - Your bad time
starts now, pray to god.

274
00:23:17,963 --> 00:23:21,262
Go slowly! - This is second installment
it has just started.

275
00:23:21,466 --> 00:23:25,766
Are you killing me in installments!
- This is 3rd round.

276
00:23:26,204 --> 00:23:30,504
Watch out, l'm doing a 7.5 on bike.
lsn't it fine? - Leave me, priest.

277
00:23:30,709 --> 00:23:34,440
l'll show you how to repent.

278
00:23:41,653 --> 00:23:42,119
Mr. Priest.

279
00:23:42,821 --> 00:23:46,450
l asked your number plate and you
made me a nameless policeman.

280
00:23:46,658 --> 00:23:48,285
That is real bad time.

281
00:23:48,827 --> 00:23:50,624
Hey! Where's my left hand?

282
00:23:51,830 --> 00:23:54,128
lt fell near Rettaipalam bridge.
Didn't you pick it up?

283
00:23:54,332 --> 00:23:57,301
You're are referring to it as a cheap pencil?
- l'll get it for you.

284
00:24:11,850 --> 00:24:14,318
Why does he never pray to
god at the temple?

285
00:24:23,695 --> 00:24:25,322
Why are you looking at
me like this?

286
00:24:25,697 --> 00:24:30,930
An astrologer told me to visit the temple
on Fridays or else l'll die.

287
00:24:31,136 --> 00:24:33,661
Otherwise why would l come
to visit this man?

288
00:24:34,706 --> 00:24:37,504
Saamy, l'll not spare you without
packing you to Singapore.

289
00:24:37,709 --> 00:24:41,509
Book a ticket to God's idol from
Tuticorin port to Singapore.

290
00:24:41,713 --> 00:24:42,179
As you say.

291
00:24:51,723 --> 00:24:53,020
He's a millionaire!

292
00:24:53,225 --> 00:24:54,783
But, his name is
Perumal Pitchai(Beggar).

293
00:24:56,061 --> 00:24:58,029
lt seems God had collected
food in alms.

294
00:24:58,230 --> 00:25:00,198
And Hanuman snatched it from his
hands & enjoyed eating it.

295
00:25:00,398 --> 00:25:04,027
But here, l'll snatch & l'll eat.

296
00:25:04,503 --> 00:25:10,533
40 years ago, l was begging
in this temple.

297
00:25:10,976 --> 00:25:15,310
So, l had changed my name from
llaya Perumal to Perumal Pitchai (Beggar).

298
00:25:15,514 --> 00:25:17,038
Enough!

299
00:25:17,749 --> 00:25:18,875
Greetings sir.

300
00:25:19,084 --> 00:25:21,882
He's garlanding a rogue
instead of god.

301
00:25:22,854 --> 00:25:26,415
Why did you garland me?
Are you changing party? - No Annachi.

302
00:25:26,758 --> 00:25:30,216
A by-election is scheduled for
SriVaikuntam. Brother needs your support.

303
00:25:30,762 --> 00:25:32,491
l've already made you two as MLA's.

304
00:25:32,697 --> 00:25:33,391
Do you want one more?

305
00:25:33,598 --> 00:25:36,999
There's only one bridge
in SriVaikuntam.

306
00:25:37,202 --> 00:25:38,829
Only one bus can go on it, at a time.

307
00:25:39,037 --> 00:25:41,403
Are you planning to bring it down?
- Nothing like that sir.

308
00:25:41,606 --> 00:25:42,903
Okay, you want to contest
the election.

309
00:25:43,608 --> 00:25:46,236
Subramani, are you doing well?
- l'm fine.

310
00:25:46,611 --> 00:25:49,239
He stole a woman's jewels when she
bent to give him alms.

311
00:25:49,447 --> 00:25:50,243
Today, he's a big shot.

312
00:25:50,615 --> 00:25:52,014
l know him very well.

313
00:25:52,384 --> 00:25:54,852
Even if l give him Rs. 10 lakhs.

314
00:25:55,053 --> 00:25:59,251
He'll make a golden begging bowl
and beg in Singapore.

315
00:26:01,126 --> 00:26:04,926
Sir, we've got information that
Coimbatore MP is going to Guruvayoor.

316
00:26:07,966 --> 00:26:11,595
A man who was hiding without
even going to Parliament.

317
00:26:12,137 --> 00:26:13,934
lf he's daring to come out, it means...

318
00:26:15,974 --> 00:26:18,442
Kill him! - Annachi, situation
is very bad.

319
00:26:18,643 --> 00:26:23,444
Are we killing for money, to be returned,
if we fail in our mission.

320
00:26:23,815 --> 00:26:26,113
Political murders must be committed
at regular intervals.

321
00:26:27,052 --> 00:26:30,112
lll fated guy! Bloody man is
going to a temple to die.

322
00:26:38,496 --> 00:26:40,665
Sir, you'll never get married?
- Why?

323
00:26:40,665 --> 00:26:41,962
You're searching
so many houses to live.

324
00:26:42,167 --> 00:26:43,634
How many girls would
you see to marry one?

325
00:26:44,002 --> 00:26:44,798
Don't worry if we
fail to get one.

326
00:26:45,003 --> 00:26:45,970
We've police quarters
as the last resort.

327
00:26:46,171 --> 00:26:48,799
This's the house mentioned
by the shop keeper.

328
00:26:54,646 --> 00:26:55,271
Whom do you want?

329
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:57,807
We've come to see a house for rent.
- Who are you?

330
00:26:58,016 --> 00:27:00,246
l'm an lnspector and he's
Deputy Commissioner.

331
00:27:06,524 --> 00:27:07,491
Just wait there.

332
00:27:07,692 --> 00:27:13,028
Grandma, last week two people stole in the
disguise of policemen, they're here.

333
00:27:13,264 --> 00:27:14,788
Yes, did you close
the door properly?

334
00:27:15,033 --> 00:27:16,830
Grandma, we must plan
and catch them.

335
00:27:17,035 --> 00:27:18,832
Why do you want to take
unnecessary risk?

336
00:27:19,537 --> 00:27:21,334
Aunt, be ready with
chili powder.

337
00:27:21,539 --> 00:27:23,166
You all come immediately,
when l call you, come grandma.

338
00:27:25,210 --> 00:27:27,178
We'll come late at nights,
there's only one way here.

339
00:27:27,379 --> 00:27:29,506
What can we do if they lock it?
- We must break the lock.

340
00:27:29,714 --> 00:27:31,011
Don't we know it?
- Didn't l tell you?

341
00:27:33,885 --> 00:27:35,352
Come...come...please.

342
00:27:35,553 --> 00:27:37,521
This is the hall,
a very large one.

343
00:27:38,223 --> 00:27:42,125
You can place the sofa,
Sit or do anything.

344
00:27:43,061 --> 00:27:44,528
Why is she speaking
like a loose (mad)?

345
00:27:44,729 --> 00:27:47,197
Yes, loose...the door latch
is little loose.

346
00:27:47,399 --> 00:27:48,525
lt'll be okay if we tighten it.

347
00:27:49,067 --> 00:27:53,026
Grandma is old, but really bold.
- They say old is gold.

348
00:27:53,405 --> 00:27:55,202
They said upstairs is vacant.
But, you're showing the downstairs.

349
00:27:55,407 --> 00:27:58,035
Our first floor and ground
floors are alike. - Yes.

350
00:27:58,243 --> 00:28:01,303
lf you see one you
needn't see another.

351
00:28:01,513 --> 00:28:03,947
This is middle of the house,
that is the store room.

352
00:28:04,149 --> 00:28:05,548
You can stock groceries.

353
00:28:05,750 --> 00:28:07,877
This is prayer room
to pray to god.

354
00:28:08,086 --> 00:28:09,383
ls the entire family mad?
- That's kitchen.

355
00:28:09,587 --> 00:28:13,148
You can cook, fry, eat or do anything.
- Clever girl.

356
00:28:13,358 --> 00:28:15,883
That is bedroom!
- You can sleep, take rest.

357
00:28:16,428 --> 00:28:19,226
You said it right, go inside
and see. - No need.

358
00:28:19,431 --> 00:28:21,899
Go inside!
- Hey why are you pushing us inside?

359
00:28:24,035 --> 00:28:26,401
Aunt...Aunt! All of you come here.
We've caught the thieves.

360
00:28:26,604 --> 00:28:28,834
Thieves! Tell them, who are we?

361
00:28:29,441 --> 00:28:30,738
How many people we would've arrested?

362
00:28:30,942 --> 00:28:32,409
Today 2 mad women
have arrested us.

363
00:28:32,777 --> 00:28:35,507
Wait, did you call the police? - Yes.

364
00:28:36,114 --> 00:28:38,082
Aunt, we are real police.

365
00:28:38,283 --> 00:28:39,750
Last week 2 guys
said the same thing.

366
00:28:39,951 --> 00:28:41,748
Aunt, please listen to me.

367
00:28:45,290 --> 00:28:45,915
What happened?

368
00:28:46,958 --> 00:28:48,926
Sir, they threw chili
powder on my face.

369
00:28:49,627 --> 00:28:50,423
Why are you laughing sir?

370
00:28:50,628 --> 00:28:52,926
What happened madam?

371
00:28:53,131 --> 00:28:55,599
Open the door carefully, 2 strong
bull like men are there. - Yes.

372
00:28:55,967 --> 00:28:56,934
Aim your rifles at them.

373
00:28:57,135 --> 00:28:58,762
Sir, will your gun fire?

374
00:28:59,804 --> 00:29:01,431
Look at the way they're
coming out, beat them.

375
00:29:01,639 --> 00:29:04,767
Sir, what's this?
- Did you call him a thief?

376
00:29:04,976 --> 00:29:06,603
He's our Deputy Commissioner.

377
00:29:07,812 --> 00:29:09,109
Deputy Commissioner?

378
00:29:09,848 --> 00:29:13,375
A mistake has been
committed unknowingly.

379
00:29:13,485 --> 00:29:14,110
Please forgive us...

380
00:29:14,319 --> 00:29:17,288
Last week, a similar incident
happened in the next street.

381
00:29:17,489 --> 00:29:18,956
That's why my grand daughter
mistook you.

382
00:29:23,361 --> 00:29:25,659
Sorry! - Forgive us.

383
00:29:27,365 --> 00:29:28,297
That is the way out.

384
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:31,125
Give me some ''idlies''...
l'll have them with this side dish.

385
00:29:40,011 --> 00:29:40,807
Greetings sir...

386
00:29:41,012 --> 00:29:41,671
Greetings sir...

387
00:29:41,846 --> 00:29:43,814
lf we leave it as it is, it'll
become a problem. - Okay...okay..

388
00:29:44,015 --> 00:29:45,312
New Deputy Commissioner
has come to see you.

389
00:29:47,852 --> 00:29:50,150
Welcome, Deputy Commissioner...

390
00:29:50,355 --> 00:29:52,585
Name...Arusaamy!
Place...Palani.

391
00:29:53,024 --> 00:29:56,653
Till now, you've been transferred to
7 places and this is your 8th place.

392
00:29:57,028 --> 00:29:58,757
You never stayed at any place
for a long time...

393
00:29:58,963 --> 00:30:00,828
You're such an honest man.

394
00:30:01,032 --> 00:30:05,833
My boys told me this place has changed
a little after your arrival.

395
00:30:06,638 --> 00:30:09,766
What are you looking at man?
l'm here ...

396
00:30:10,041 --> 00:30:13,169
But l'm aware of all that's happening
in every nook & corner of lndia.

397
00:30:13,378 --> 00:30:17,439
But nobody knows about me...
- l know...

398
00:30:18,116 --> 00:30:21,085
Your original name is llaya Perumal,
63 years old, native place, Vallanadu.

399
00:30:21,953 --> 00:30:24,513
Out of 123 wine shops in Tirunelveli,

400
00:30:24,722 --> 00:30:27,247
You own 1 16 shops including
36 illegal shops.

401
00:30:27,792 --> 00:30:29,123
Out of 80 lorries quarrying
sand from river Tamarabarani,

402
00:30:29,327 --> 00:30:30,419
You own 75 lorries.

403
00:30:30,962 --> 00:30:32,691
30 of them are running illegally.

404
00:30:33,131 --> 00:30:35,599
18 omni buses plying to out stations
are without permits.

405
00:30:36,467 --> 00:30:38,594
You own many lodges
under fictitious names.

406
00:30:38,970 --> 00:30:40,528
They're being used for
illegal activities.

407
00:30:41,306 --> 00:30:44,104
You've 3 ships in Tuticorin & 2 cracker
factories in Sivakasi. Apart from these,

408
00:30:44,309 --> 00:30:46,004
Which ever party may come to power...

409
00:30:46,644 --> 00:30:47,975
ln the 8 districts of south,

410
00:30:48,246 --> 00:30:51,113
You select the winning &
losing MLA's & MP's.

411
00:30:53,084 --> 00:30:55,279
Perumal Pitchai, kingmaker.

412
00:30:57,989 --> 00:30:59,786
But your name will never be published
in the newspaper...

413
00:30:59,991 --> 00:31:01,219
Your posters will never be seen.

414
00:31:01,426 --> 00:31:04,122
After knowing all this, you won't
leave me without taking action.

415
00:31:04,329 --> 00:31:05,796
But, if you take action
l won't spare you.

416
00:31:05,997 --> 00:31:07,624
You won't take bribe also.

417
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:11,298
Which place you want to
be transferred? Tell me.

418
00:31:11,669 --> 00:31:14,035
l'll help you...
- Who said that l won't take bribes?

419
00:31:14,606 --> 00:31:15,971
My henchmen.

420
00:31:16,174 --> 00:31:18,142
Hey! Give him a chair.
Go & bring it.

421
00:31:19,844 --> 00:31:20,640
How much can you offer?

422
00:31:20,945 --> 00:31:22,139
How much you want?

423
00:31:22,347 --> 00:31:25,976
l want to do my duty.
l need your help for that.

424
00:31:26,184 --> 00:31:26,980
l didn't get you.

425
00:31:27,185 --> 00:31:28,812
ln city, your lorries
always cross speed limit,

426
00:31:29,020 --> 00:31:30,317
and are frequently involved
in accidents.

427
00:31:30,622 --> 00:31:32,988
They should be
within city speed limits.

428
00:31:33,858 --> 00:31:34,483
Despite knowing, drinking liquor is
injurious to health, they drink.

429
00:31:34,692 --> 00:31:36,319
l'm not bothered about them.

430
00:31:36,694 --> 00:31:39,595
But if a drunkard creates a scene
on the road, l'll not spare him.

431
00:31:39,731 --> 00:31:41,596
Your henchmen shouldn't come to me
for taking them out on bail.

432
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:44,168
l'm not bothered about your
illegal businesses.

433
00:31:44,602 --> 00:31:47,230
But you should control local goons
who use your name.

434
00:31:47,538 --> 00:31:49,665
Or else, l may have to control them
and you shouldn't get angry with me.

435
00:31:50,375 --> 00:31:52,502
l don't care about your
illegal wine shops.

436
00:31:53,044 --> 00:31:56,775
But, you've 7 shops near schools & temples
which are troublesome to people.

437
00:31:56,981 --> 00:31:58,448
l'm not asking you to
close down those shops.

438
00:31:58,983 --> 00:32:00,075
You can shift them to
some other place.

439
00:32:03,721 --> 00:32:06,849
lf you agree to this,
l'll accept your money.

440
00:32:07,558 --> 00:32:12,359
l think what you said is right.

441
00:32:13,064 --> 00:32:15,032
Okay, l'll make arrangements.

442
00:32:15,733 --> 00:32:17,701
Hey! Give him...take it...

443
00:32:23,741 --> 00:32:24,366
l'll take leave...

444
00:32:26,077 --> 00:32:26,543
Brother...

445
00:32:28,012 --> 00:32:31,038
You said you're from Palani...
What is the caste you said...

446
00:32:31,416 --> 00:32:32,041
l didn't say.

447
00:32:36,587 --> 00:32:39,385
Sir, what's this?
Why did you act like a`Yes man'?

448
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:44,050
He seems to be from our caste.
- What do you mean?

449
00:32:44,662 --> 00:32:46,630
Did you hear his brave words?

450
00:32:46,931 --> 00:32:48,558
So, do we've to obey
all his commands?

451
00:32:49,767 --> 00:32:52,133
He was not ordering us.
He told us politely.

452
00:32:52,503 --> 00:32:54,903
His predecessors went against us.

453
00:32:55,106 --> 00:32:57,074
Or else, they took bribe and
ruined the town.

454
00:32:57,275 --> 00:32:58,902
He's different to them.

455
00:32:59,110 --> 00:33:02,739
Not only that we are also facing
problems in those 7 shops.

456
00:33:03,114 --> 00:33:04,240
let's shift them & see.

457
00:33:06,884 --> 00:33:10,615
What's this? Why do you create so much
smoke like a dream sequence?

458
00:33:11,789 --> 00:33:14,758
Shut up. Can't you
cut your hair?

459
00:33:14,959 --> 00:33:17,257
Shut up! This's going to be
a fashion in 2005.

460
00:33:17,462 --> 00:33:20,522
Watch out! Even Capt. Vijaykanth
will sport this hair style.

461
00:33:20,732 --> 00:33:22,757
Not only that, for all priests,

462
00:33:22,967 --> 00:33:25,936
it's traditional to sport
such a hair style...

463
00:33:26,237 --> 00:33:27,761
Are you atleast doing that properly?

464
00:33:28,072 --> 00:33:30,768
Wherever you go, you create trouble.
- What to do?

465
00:33:31,075 --> 00:33:33,009
Last week, the marriage which
l had attended as a priest,

466
00:33:33,211 --> 00:33:34,371
at the time of giving
the auspicious thread,

467
00:33:34,579 --> 00:33:37,104
l saw the groom's face
and got shocked...

468
00:33:37,315 --> 00:33:41,115
l had performed that rascal's
marriage a month earlier.

469
00:33:41,319 --> 00:33:42,377
l was tensed.

470
00:33:42,653 --> 00:33:44,951
l took a brick from
sacrificial fire,

471
00:33:45,156 --> 00:33:47,954
asked him, ''How many girl's lives
are you going to ruin'',

472
00:33:48,326 --> 00:33:50,123
l threw it on his face.

473
00:33:50,328 --> 00:33:52,455
That's all.
He started to bleed profusely.

474
00:33:52,663 --> 00:33:53,789
Then, it stopped.

475
00:33:53,998 --> 00:33:54,794
Did the bleeding stop?

476
00:33:54,999 --> 00:33:56,125
No...marriage was stopped.

477
00:33:56,334 --> 00:33:59,997
lt's enough if you perform your job
properly without creating problem today.

478
00:34:00,204 --> 00:34:02,138
You knot the hair soon...
l'll conduct it excellently...

479
00:34:02,340 --> 00:34:02,806
l've already done it.

480
00:34:02,940 --> 00:34:05,238
Rogues are not traveling on the
foot-board these days.

481
00:34:05,443 --> 00:34:06,910
After the arrival of D.C. Arusaamy...

482
00:34:07,111 --> 00:34:09,579
lf they do, they're beaten black & blue.

483
00:34:09,781 --> 00:34:11,942
Oh God! l've lost my chain...

484
00:34:12,116 --> 00:34:13,583
Driver, go to the police station...

485
00:34:17,889 --> 00:34:19,015
Check every one.

486
00:34:19,624 --> 00:34:20,921
Don't spare anyone.

487
00:34:21,726 --> 00:34:22,454
Brahmin girl!

488
00:34:23,895 --> 00:34:25,522
Stand in a line.

489
00:34:26,064 --> 00:34:28,532
Can't you recognize a thief by face?
Do we look like thieves?

490
00:34:28,733 --> 00:34:30,724
Didn't you throw
chili powder on our faces?

491
00:34:32,403 --> 00:34:34,371
Hey! What's happening there?
- Sir, chain snatching...

492
00:34:34,739 --> 00:34:36,206
They are making even girls
to stand in a line.

493
00:34:45,116 --> 00:34:46,708
Why is he staring at us?

494
00:34:49,754 --> 00:34:51,381
Show me your bag.
- We are getting late to college.

495
00:34:51,622 --> 00:34:53,055
First check us...

496
00:34:53,257 --> 00:34:54,656
Paramasivam, send them first.

497
00:34:54,926 --> 00:34:56,985
Women police are coming
to check women.

498
00:34:57,261 --> 00:34:58,888
When will they come
and when will we go?

499
00:34:59,097 --> 00:34:59,995
lt's alright, send them.

500
00:35:00,198 --> 00:35:02,723
Sir, l'll not allow anyone
to disturb me in my duty.

501
00:35:02,934 --> 00:35:04,925
Because, l'm not a police man
but a rogue.

502
00:35:05,269 --> 00:35:08,705
You can go...
- What about the bus?

503
00:35:09,040 --> 00:35:10,564
Bus will go after checking every one.

504
00:35:11,008 --> 00:35:13,238
Then, how will we go?
- Go by an auto.

505
00:35:13,978 --> 00:35:14,535
Money?

506
00:35:14,745 --> 00:35:18,841
Don't you carry Rs.20, while going
to the college? - Rs.20!

507
00:35:19,050 --> 00:35:20,642
We've a student bus pass.

508
00:35:20,852 --> 00:35:23,753
lf by chance we lose it,
we've Rs.5 for to & fro fare.

509
00:35:23,955 --> 00:35:25,946
We've curd rice & pickle for lunch.

510
00:35:26,157 --> 00:35:28,591
Apart from this, why should a
college girl carry money?

511
00:35:29,060 --> 00:35:30,789
Okay, l'll give you money.

512
00:35:31,062 --> 00:35:34,429
Hey! Call an auto.
- We don't want other's money.

513
00:35:34,632 --> 00:35:37,499
Okay, take it as loan
& repay it later.

514
00:35:40,538 --> 00:35:42,199
His mind is getting distracted.

515
00:35:42,573 --> 00:35:47,704
Sir, my wife isn't happy
about my late coming.

516
00:35:47,912 --> 00:35:48,776
Atleast today let's go early.

517
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:50,914
Wait, let the night show be over.

518
00:35:51,415 --> 00:35:54,282
He'll neither marry & enjoy
nor allow me to enjoy.

519
00:35:54,485 --> 00:35:55,452
Why are you blabbering?

520
00:35:56,387 --> 00:35:59,049
l was talking about the
greatness of bachelor's life.

521
00:35:59,457 --> 00:36:01,789
Who's that?
Where are you coming from?

522
00:36:02,059 --> 00:36:03,526
Sir, we went to a movie.
- Movie?

523
00:36:03,728 --> 00:36:05,457
Didn't your husbands come with you?

524
00:36:05,663 --> 00:36:06,322
No Sir.

525
00:36:06,531 --> 00:36:08,123
Where is your house? - Vagedu.

526
00:36:08,332 --> 00:36:10,266
Vagedu?...Are you going there
alone at this late hour?

527
00:36:10,468 --> 00:36:12,231
Take this torch.
- No, it's alright.

528
00:36:12,436 --> 00:36:13,528
lt's alright, take it.

529
00:36:13,738 --> 00:36:15,603
Ask your husband to return it
in the station tomorrow.

530
00:36:15,806 --> 00:36:18,400
Take it. - Okay sir, bye.

531
00:36:21,345 --> 00:36:23,745
Sir take it. You've helped my wife.
Thank you very much.

532
00:36:23,948 --> 00:36:26,781
Wife? Hey! Are you a man?

533
00:36:26,984 --> 00:36:29,919
Neither you were courageous to take
your wife to the night show,

534
00:36:30,121 --> 00:36:32,817
Nor you had the guts to
stop her from going alone.

535
00:36:33,024 --> 00:36:34,218
Then, why did you marry?

536
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:36,390
After not stopping her from
going alone,

537
00:36:36,594 --> 00:36:39,324
You complain that she has been
robbed, raped, murdered etc..

538
00:36:39,530 --> 00:36:42,499
Hey! There are 550 million women
in our country.

539
00:36:42,700 --> 00:36:44,497
ls it possible to provide police
security to every woman?

540
00:36:44,702 --> 00:36:47,170
Paramasivam, hereafter you arrest
all the husbands,

541
00:36:47,305 --> 00:36:49,671
Who send their wives alone to
movies. - Yes sir.

542
00:36:49,974 --> 00:36:52,636
lf he had married, he would've known
the problem of a husband. - What?

543
00:36:52,877 --> 00:36:54,572
Sir, nothing. l just tested whether
this torch is working or not.

544
00:36:54,879 --> 00:37:00,044
A white cat is living
in my house.

545
00:37:00,651 --> 00:37:02,448
What's this Hubby?
Who are they?

546
00:37:02,653 --> 00:37:07,989
They're very tired children.
Serve them food.

547
00:37:08,192 --> 00:37:10,786
Oh God! lt's a great sin.
- Sin?

548
00:37:17,802 --> 00:37:20,168
Why grandpa is shouting like this?
- Did he get a stroke?

549
00:37:20,371 --> 00:37:22,134
Don't blabber. They're offering
food to the crows.

550
00:37:22,340 --> 00:37:24,900
You'll offer food to the crows.
Won't you offer it to them?

551
00:37:25,109 --> 00:37:27,202
Crows are our forefathers,
our ancestors.

552
00:37:27,411 --> 00:37:30,380
Ancestors? ls an ordinary crow
your grandfather?

553
00:37:30,581 --> 00:37:32,606
ls Raven, your great grand father?

554
00:37:32,817 --> 00:37:34,375
Whom are you fooling?

555
00:37:34,585 --> 00:37:38,715
Hey! Don't criticize the traditions,
you fool. - Forgive me grandpa.

556
00:37:38,923 --> 00:37:41,915
Crows may satiate their hunger
by picking or stealing food.

557
00:37:42,126 --> 00:37:45,323
Blue cross also protects them.

558
00:37:45,529 --> 00:37:49,966
But for the poor & uneducated
like them,

559
00:37:50,167 --> 00:37:52,795
White cross like us are
here to help.

560
00:37:53,004 --> 00:37:55,268
Grandpa, do you know, because
of the food you offer to crows,

561
00:37:55,473 --> 00:37:57,270
How many problems politicians
have to face?

562
00:37:57,475 --> 00:37:58,100
What do you mean?

563
00:37:58,309 --> 00:38:00,277
lt eats gravy food here,

564
00:38:00,478 --> 00:38:03,970
And a rotten `Masal vada'
from a shop,

565
00:38:04,181 --> 00:38:07,673
Mutton piece
from a mutton shop.

566
00:38:07,885 --> 00:38:10,149
Eating all this, its stomach
gets upset.

567
00:38:10,354 --> 00:38:13,585
Lastly they go & sit over
the Politician's head,

568
00:38:13,791 --> 00:38:15,588
And shit like this.

569
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:19,227
Don't you've Rs.50? What's this man?
...Go, man...

570
00:38:26,037 --> 00:38:28,267
Sir, l asked for his license
and he said `No'.

571
00:38:28,472 --> 00:38:29,632
That's why, l warned him.

572
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:31,102
l believe...l believe you...

573
00:38:31,642 --> 00:38:33,166
Why do you ask Rs.50 and
insult the police?

574
00:38:33,377 --> 00:38:36,039
You ask Rs.500. To escape from the
trouble, he'll take a license,

575
00:38:36,247 --> 00:38:37,544
And you can also avoid
asking bribes frequently.

576
00:38:38,749 --> 00:38:42,412
ls he asking me take bribe or not?
l don't get him.

577
00:38:46,691 --> 00:38:48,181
Why are you dull for the
past 2 days?

578
00:38:48,693 --> 00:38:51,389
Hey! DC is there, l'll return
the auto fare.

579
00:38:52,363 --> 00:38:55,924
Bus may start...
- l'll come back before that.

580
00:38:57,268 --> 00:38:58,997
When will it be finished?
- The judgement is on 10th of next month.

581
00:38:59,203 --> 00:39:02,195
You said, it's one day's work.
Remind me about it. - Yes sir.

582
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:03,802
Hello, What's it?

583
00:39:04,008 --> 00:39:08,604
That day you gave me Rs.22.50
as auto fare, take it...

584
00:39:08,813 --> 00:39:13,011
lt was Rs.45, why're you giving me
only Rs.22.50? - Rs.45?

585
00:39:13,351 --> 00:39:18,345
Metre showed only Rs.22.50...
- He asked me for the return fare of Rs.22.50.

586
00:39:18,556 --> 00:39:19,523
Oh God!

587
00:39:19,724 --> 00:39:24,184
To repay Rs.22.50, l was
sleepless for 2 days.

588
00:39:24,395 --> 00:39:26,522
l packed chili powder
in 60 packets.

589
00:39:27,832 --> 00:39:32,098
Oh God! l missed the bus.
How will l go now? - You go by an auto.

590
00:39:32,303 --> 00:39:34,965
What about the auto fare?
- How many of you've started this business?

591
00:39:35,172 --> 00:39:38,141
You may not have much money,
but only Rs.5 for bus fare.

592
00:39:38,342 --> 00:39:39,604
For lunch, you would've curd rice
& pickle.

593
00:39:39,810 --> 00:39:42,540
No, today l've sambar rice & `pulse'
curry. - Let it be anything.

594
00:39:43,013 --> 00:39:45,038
You'll say that why does a college girl
need money more than this?

595
00:39:45,249 --> 00:39:47,774
Take it back. Keep your cash bag
with yourself.

596
00:39:48,018 --> 00:39:48,950
Hey! Auto...

597
00:39:52,223 --> 00:39:54,214
Your money... - Repay the total
money later.

598
00:39:55,459 --> 00:39:56,050
Hey! Wait.

599
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:58,091
What's your name? - Sir, Murugan.

600
00:39:58,295 --> 00:39:59,887
Which area? - Pettai.

601
00:40:00,131 --> 00:40:01,723
You know the station phone number?
- Yes sir.

602
00:40:01,932 --> 00:40:03,991
lnform me on phone after dropping her.
- Okay sir. - Go.

603
00:40:08,372 --> 00:40:09,703
Dhanam brother. - Yes sir.

604
00:40:10,408 --> 00:40:11,670
You follow that auto.

605
00:40:11,876 --> 00:40:13,002
Why did he ask you to
phone him?

606
00:40:13,210 --> 00:40:16,304
l look like a rowdy, don't l?
That's why, he suspects me.

607
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:21,083
ls DCP your relative? He's very concerned
about you! - Nothing like that.

608
00:40:21,519 --> 00:40:24,283
Then, why is he sending a
constable to follow us?

609
00:40:28,225 --> 00:40:30,819
After Saamy sir's arrival, Tirunelveli
junction is entirely changed.

610
00:40:31,028 --> 00:40:32,893
All those vandals on roads have
gone into hibernation.

611
00:40:33,097 --> 00:40:35,565
Wow, whether the auto runs or not,
metre runs perfectly...

612
00:40:35,766 --> 00:40:38,234
He's an honest man...

613
00:40:49,647 --> 00:40:51,706
Do you know how much
he's concerned about me?

614
00:40:51,949 --> 00:40:55,043
Don't move around with a policeman. Forget it,
or else l'll inform aunt.

615
00:40:55,453 --> 00:40:59,287
You tell aunt or Saamy (god).
- Again Saamy!

616
00:40:59,490 --> 00:41:02,220
He's a good person...
He's an honest man.

617
00:41:02,426 --> 00:41:04,792
Bhuvana, do you know who's the guest
for tomorrow's function?

618
00:41:04,995 --> 00:41:06,622
Deputy Commissioner Saamy!

619
00:41:12,803 --> 00:41:15,101
What's it Annachi?
You've made me jobless.

620
00:41:15,306 --> 00:41:17,206
Earlier atleast once in a month
we used to hear the blasts.

621
00:41:17,408 --> 00:41:19,535
Now, there's no sound and l feel as
if l've become deaf.

622
00:41:19,743 --> 00:41:22,473
Don't you know anything else
other than planting bombs?

623
00:41:23,481 --> 00:41:27,850
l've made you the proprietor of a
35 acre crackers factory in Sivakasi.

624
00:41:28,052 --> 00:41:31,579
You're standing here like a lamp post
leaving behind your brain in Sivakasi.

625
00:41:31,789 --> 00:41:34,952
A dog will always remain loyal
to lick it's boss's feet.

626
00:41:35,159 --> 00:41:37,389
lf we allow him, he may plant
a bomb here itself.

627
00:41:37,595 --> 00:41:39,028
First send him to Sivakasi.

628
00:41:39,230 --> 00:41:40,424
Brother, come let's go
to bus station.

629
00:41:40,631 --> 00:41:41,996
l'll call you when l need you.

630
00:41:44,134 --> 00:41:45,567
Greetings, sir... - Greeting sir...

631
00:41:46,470 --> 00:41:47,095
Annachi...

632
00:41:47,304 --> 00:41:48,168
He is taking bath.

633
00:41:50,541 --> 00:41:52,475
Generally people can hold breath
for 2 minutes under water.

634
00:41:52,877 --> 00:41:55,345
But Annachi can hold for 10 minutes.

635
00:41:58,182 --> 00:41:59,672
Welcome Saamy.

636
00:42:00,484 --> 00:42:01,576
What are you looking at?

637
00:42:02,119 --> 00:42:03,950
Surprised as to how l know about
your arrival?

638
00:42:04,388 --> 00:42:10,190
Even from under 10 feet water,
l can recognize anyone.

639
00:42:10,394 --> 00:42:12,862
l'm used to take bath here
since my childhood.

640
00:42:13,063 --> 00:42:15,827
Neither l know it's virtues
nor sins..

641
00:42:20,437 --> 00:42:22,462
l made him a MLA.

642
00:42:22,673 --> 00:42:24,732
But, he made tall promises that
he'll give this & that,

643
00:42:24,942 --> 00:42:26,603
Sanction water supply etc.,
on the stage.

644
00:42:26,810 --> 00:42:29,711
Believing him, farmers are
waiting with their implements.

645
00:42:29,914 --> 00:42:34,317
Even CM used to ask me before
saying anything on the stage.

646
00:42:34,518 --> 00:42:36,543
He went over board.

647
00:42:36,787 --> 00:42:40,188
Tirunelveli is receiving Tamarabarani
water after l take my bath in it.

648
00:42:41,091 --> 00:42:42,422
Saamy, don't mistake me.

649
00:42:42,626 --> 00:42:45,891
l'm a friendly type but if l
get angry, l'll not spare anybody.

650
00:42:46,096 --> 00:42:48,656
All having Tata Sumos,
Qualis etc.,

651
00:42:48,866 --> 00:42:51,391
Are you wondering why l'm
still using Ambassador?

652
00:42:51,769 --> 00:42:54,397
Astrologer told me that if l lose
this car my life will be in danger.

653
00:42:54,638 --> 00:42:57,539
Nagarajan of 75th ward is
troubling us using your name.

654
00:42:57,808 --> 00:43:00,971
Hey! Who's that rascal? Playing politics
without our knowledge!

655
00:43:01,378 --> 00:43:02,345
Ask him to meet me...

656
00:43:03,447 --> 00:43:04,914
l'll take care of him, you go.
- l'll get along.

657
00:43:05,382 --> 00:43:08,408
He's the right man. He consults me
& does everything...

658
00:43:08,886 --> 00:43:14,415
District Magistrate who's the Chief Guest
here on this lndependence day..

659
00:43:14,625 --> 00:43:17,924
After you've come to Tirunelveli
crime rate has come down a lot.

660
00:43:18,896 --> 00:43:21,091
Whatever help you want, tell me...

661
00:43:21,632 --> 00:43:24,396
As a Judge, l'll definitely do the
needful. - Thank you sir.

662
00:43:24,635 --> 00:43:29,095
l'll request the Deputy Commissioner
Arusaamy to give a speech.

663
00:43:30,975 --> 00:43:33,535
l like Tirunelveli ''Halwa''.

664
00:43:33,811 --> 00:43:35,438
Becareful, he might cheat you.

665
00:43:37,982 --> 00:43:40,382
l like girls in this town
more than that.

666
00:43:42,152 --> 00:43:42,948
Don't mistake me.

667
00:43:43,654 --> 00:43:44,678
l like your courage...

668
00:43:45,656 --> 00:43:47,783
ln this town, the way the
girls carry umbrellas,

669
00:43:48,158 --> 00:43:50,626
l feel as if they're
carrying sickles.

670
00:43:53,497 --> 00:43:56,625
Normally, men will trouble women.

671
00:43:56,834 --> 00:43:59,962
He may be a thief or a rogue.
You shouldn't get scared of them.

672
00:44:00,270 --> 00:44:01,965
l'm not asking you to carry
weapons for self protection.

673
00:44:02,339 --> 00:44:03,465
Even chili powder in
your house will do.

674
00:44:04,274 --> 00:44:06,640
l've the experience of being attacked
by the chili powder.

675
00:44:06,844 --> 00:44:07,970
Hey! He's referring to you.

676
00:44:08,345 --> 00:44:11,143
ln this town, when we went in search
of a house in civil dress, a girl...

677
00:44:14,018 --> 00:44:16,486
A girl mistook us as thieves
and locked us inside a room.

678
00:44:17,021 --> 00:44:17,988
She threw chili powder on us.

679
00:44:18,188 --> 00:44:19,587
She's a student of
your college.

680
00:44:19,790 --> 00:44:21,417
Who's she?

681
00:44:21,625 --> 00:44:24,822
The girl wearing black
upper cloth...that girl.

682
00:44:26,030 --> 00:44:26,826
lt's you only.

683
00:44:27,197 --> 00:44:28,596
lt'll be better if you come on
the dais yourself.

684
00:44:28,799 --> 00:44:34,829
He's calling you.
Go...go.

685
00:44:37,041 --> 00:44:38,508
Bhuvana, please come to the stage.

686
00:44:40,377 --> 00:44:42,675
On behalf of our Police Department,
l appreciate her.

687
00:44:48,218 --> 00:44:49,845
l like her bravery.

688
00:44:51,388 --> 00:44:52,685
l like her intelligence.

689
00:44:57,394 --> 00:44:59,191
l like it...l like it very much.

690
00:45:05,602 --> 00:45:34,057
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

691
00:45:34,531 --> 00:45:41,437
Oh God! You like me.

692
00:45:41,638 --> 00:45:48,441
l too like you.

693
00:45:48,645 --> 00:45:55,414
l like your courage &
your liking me.

694
00:45:55,619 --> 00:45:58,452
l like you innocence.

695
00:45:58,655 --> 00:46:02,421
l like the eyes which
stole me.

696
00:46:02,626 --> 00:46:09,464
l'm new to this trade
of stealing.

697
00:46:09,666 --> 00:46:13,227
l'm not able to steal
it fully & cleanly.

698
00:46:28,652 --> 00:47:01,681
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

699
00:47:02,319 --> 00:47:09,157
l like your lips which are like
the couplet of Thiruvalluvar.

700
00:47:09,359 --> 00:47:15,923
l like the act played by
your lips near my ears.

701
