He'll foist a theft case
on your father.

933
01:01:51,607 --> 01:01:53,939
He'll brand your sister as prostitute
and ruin your entire family.

934
01:01:54,143 --> 01:01:56,509
So, do we've to endure all this?
- You've to.

935
01:01:57,046 --> 01:01:58,013
You're waiting patiently in a queue
for kerosene in a ration shop,

936
01:01:58,214 --> 01:02:01,672
And for tickets in a theatre.
How can you get instant justice?

937
01:02:02,218 --> 01:02:03,515
lf the case goes to Court,

938
01:02:03,720 --> 01:02:09,352
They'll put embarrassing questions
and kill that girl alive.

939
01:02:09,826 --> 01:02:12,192
A secret between us will
become an open secret.

940
01:02:12,395 --> 01:02:13,521
Then, isn't there any way
to get justice?

941
01:02:13,730 --> 01:02:16,858
Putting such rogues in jail isn't
just punishment for them.

942
01:02:17,567 --> 01:02:20,866
Against Law, we must stone him to death
or shoot him to death publicly.

943
01:02:22,071 --> 01:02:24,539
Such a situation will come,
then l'll give you a sickle.

944
01:02:24,741 --> 01:02:27,369
Till then, retain this anger on him.
- Sir, Annachi has called you.

945
01:02:29,912 --> 01:02:31,504
Tell him, l'll come. - He has asked you
to come immediately, sir.

946
01:02:31,581 --> 01:02:32,377
Rascal!

947
01:02:34,417 --> 01:02:35,179
Bloody!

948
01:02:43,993 --> 01:02:45,620
What do you think of me?

949
01:02:46,262 --> 01:02:48,890
Am l your servant or
your broom?

950
01:02:49,098 --> 01:02:50,895
He's calling me authoritatively
as if l'm his watchman.

951
01:02:51,601 --> 01:02:54,229
l've self esteem & self respect. l'll not
give them up under any circumstances.

952
01:02:54,937 --> 01:02:57,303
The money you pay me is fee
for the mistakes you commit.

953
01:02:57,607 --> 01:02:59,575
lt's a price for not
doing my duty.

954
01:03:00,943 --> 01:03:02,740
l'll respect only Perumal Pitchai.

955
01:03:02,945 --> 01:03:05,243
l don't care for any other beggar
who begs from him.

956
01:03:05,448 --> 01:03:09,077
lf you still do it, l'll pump bullets
into everyone of you here.

957
01:03:10,586 --> 01:03:12,315
King will kill on the same day.
God will kill leisurely,

958
01:03:12,455 --> 01:03:15,049
And l'll kill without leaving
any evidence. Be careful.

959
01:03:15,591 --> 01:03:17,957
Annachi, he's abusing us loudly and
you're watching.

960
01:03:18,294 --> 01:03:21,821
He's definitely from our caste only.

961
01:03:22,298 --> 01:03:25,495
When he was speaking in anger,
his ears turned red. Did you see?

962
01:03:25,701 --> 01:03:28,101
He meant all of us and
you're talking about his caste.

963
01:03:29,305 --> 01:03:30,272
l had told you to call him.

964
01:03:30,473 --> 01:03:31,997
Did you cross the limits and
invited trouble here?

965
01:03:32,408 --> 01:03:36,435
A Tiger will crouch to pounce
on the prey. Be careful.

966
01:03:37,713 --> 01:03:39,180
Hey, stop the jeep.

967
01:03:40,049 --> 01:03:41,846
Why is she standing here without
going to college?

968
01:03:44,554 --> 01:03:45,612
Sir, where're you now?

969
01:03:45,822 --> 01:03:46,846
l'm on my way to
Commissioner's office.

970
01:03:47,223 --> 01:03:48,349
lsn't that chili powder
girl there..

971
01:03:48,558 --> 01:03:49,422
Yes, so what?

972
01:03:49,625 --> 01:03:51,752
She's standing at the bus stop for a
long time. Did you ask her to come?

973
01:03:51,961 --> 01:03:53,087
Okay...l'm coming there immediately.

974
01:03:53,563 --> 01:03:54,530
Then, Commissioner?

975
01:03:54,730 --> 01:03:55,526
l'll meet him later.

976
01:03:56,232 --> 01:03:57,199
That's it.

977
01:03:57,733 --> 01:03:59,360
When it comes to love
even God will falter.

978
01:03:59,635 --> 01:04:02,195
Can Saamy stay away from faltering?
Start the jeep.

979
01:04:21,090 --> 01:04:21,988
Why're you standing here?

980
01:04:22,191 --> 01:04:23,158
l want to talk to you...

981
01:04:36,439 --> 01:04:37,201
About what?

982
01:04:40,276 --> 01:04:41,243
Why didn't you come for
the last 4 days?

983
01:04:42,178 --> 01:04:44,169
l went to Madurai for
CM's programme, why?

984
01:04:46,949 --> 01:04:48,883
What happened?
Why're you crying?

985
01:04:50,686 --> 01:04:52,244
l feel lost without seeing you.

986
01:04:53,456 --> 01:04:54,923
l feel like seeing
you every day.

987
01:04:56,125 --> 01:04:58,093
l want to be always with you.

988
01:04:59,128 --> 01:05:02,097
Okay, hereafter, you'll always
be with me only.

989
01:05:03,132 --> 01:05:03,598
How?

990
01:05:03,799 --> 01:05:04,766
lf l marry you, won't you be always
with me?

991
01:05:06,302 --> 01:05:07,098
Will you marry me?

992
01:05:08,471 --> 01:05:08,937
Yes.

993
01:05:10,306 --> 01:05:10,772
Really?

994
01:05:11,974 --> 01:05:12,941
l'll definitely marry you.

995
01:05:15,144 --> 01:05:40,664
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

996
01:05:40,970 --> 01:05:46,840
Shall we marry and then elope
or shall we elope & then marry?

997
01:05:59,322 --> 01:06:01,950
Shall we marry and then
have children,

998
01:06:02,158 --> 01:06:05,286
Or shall we have children
and then marry?

999
01:06:05,494 --> 01:06:08,292
You're a girl grown
in fragrance...

1000
01:06:08,497 --> 01:06:11,466
You're a fair complexioned
grown up girl.

1001
01:06:11,834 --> 01:06:14,462
There's no date that'll
suit Saamy.

1002
01:06:14,670 --> 01:06:17,639
lt's not justice to quote
silly reasons.

1003
01:06:30,219 --> 01:07:03,749
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

1004
01:07:04,387 --> 01:07:10,019
You speak & look tasteful.
Can you cook tastefully?

1005
01:07:10,393 --> 01:07:16,263
Shall l boil red gram in milk,
make it a paste & serve you?

1006
01:07:16,599 --> 01:07:22,538
Did l ask you for a patient's diet?
l had asked, can you cook spicy food?

1007
01:07:22,738 --> 01:07:28,540
l can prepare pepper soup
with red chili, taste it.

1008
01:07:28,744 --> 01:07:34,546
Can you prepare crab, chicken
and mutton soup?

1009
01:07:34,750 --> 01:07:41,053
There's spice in my waist.
Come and relish it as you wish.

1010
01:07:53,803 --> 01:08:17,320
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

1011
01:08:18,327 --> 01:08:23,856
You're threatening me with your
big moustache like ''Ayyanar''.

1012
01:08:24,400 --> 01:08:30,202
Why're you hesitating like a hen
to jump over the fence to hatch eggs?

1013
01:08:30,406 --> 01:08:33,534
Only after our marriage is fixed,

1014
01:08:39,682 --> 01:08:42,116
l'll jump the fence.
Do as you wish.

1015
01:08:42,818 --> 01:08:48,381
l'll present you with a gift if you
adjust a little before marriage.

1016
01:08:48,591 --> 01:08:51,560
lf l take a turmeric bath,
desires overtake me.

1017
01:08:51,760 --> 01:08:54,558
lf l see you, my body
is getting thrilled.

1018
01:08:54,763 --> 01:09:03,137
Shall l come to gossip with you
or stay with you all night?

1019
01:09:19,388 --> 01:09:46,910
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

1020
01:09:49,585 --> 01:09:51,052
Sir, my son was driving the car.

1021
01:09:51,220 --> 01:09:53,017
The cyclist crossed his path
and fell under his car.

1022
01:09:53,222 --> 01:09:54,689
You must help us.

1023
01:09:55,991 --> 01:09:56,787
Give Rs.4 lakhs.

1024
01:09:57,993 --> 01:09:59,085
Why're you forcing me
to marry now?

1025
01:09:59,328 --> 01:10:01,091
lf you feel l'm a
burden to you,

1026
01:10:01,397 --> 01:10:03,797
l'll drown myself to death
in the river. - Shut up.

1027
01:10:03,999 --> 01:10:05,864
Which river has water
for you to drown?

1028
01:10:06,068 --> 01:10:07,535
Only lorries transporting sand
are plying on river beds.

1029
01:10:07,736 --> 01:10:09,363
Why're you biting nails now?

1030
01:10:09,572 --> 01:10:11,039
l feel like biting you
just like this.

1031
01:10:11,240 --> 01:10:13,538
l'm not able to understand your sister,
do you also want to join?

1032
01:10:13,742 --> 01:10:17,701
lf you like, marry or else
l'll send them back.

1033
01:10:17,913 --> 01:10:19,881
No need, they've liked
you very much.

1034
01:10:20,082 --> 01:10:22,209
lf father agrees, we can fix
the date of marriage.

1035
01:10:26,922 --> 01:10:28,219
Hello. - Tell me, chili powder.

1036
01:10:28,424 --> 01:10:29,550
A prospective groom has
come to see me.

1037
01:10:30,025 --> 01:10:31,890
From which place? - Papanasam.

1038
01:10:32,094 --> 01:10:35,393
Good place. There's a dam there.
You can take good bath.

1039
01:10:36,098 --> 01:10:37,224
Did you like the groom?

1040
01:10:37,433 --> 01:10:39,731
l'm serious, are you
making fun of me?

1041
01:10:40,102 --> 01:10:41,569
They're going to fix
the date shortly.

1042
01:10:41,770 --> 01:10:44,068
Tell me if they fix it.
l'll create trouble immediately.

1043
01:10:44,440 --> 01:10:45,566
How can you come immediately?

1044
01:10:46,775 --> 01:10:47,673
l'm outside your house.

1045
01:10:52,114 --> 01:10:53,411
Shall l come in and
create trouble?

1046
01:10:54,450 --> 01:10:56,918
l'm not scared any more
about anything.

1047
01:10:57,453 --> 01:10:59,751
l became more confident
after seeing you.

1048
01:11:04,860 --> 01:11:06,088
l'm not interested in
this marriage.

1049
01:11:06,295 --> 01:11:09,423
Look, we are in no way inferior
to you in anything.

1050
01:11:09,632 --> 01:11:11,099
My son is working in
R.T.O. Office.

1051
01:11:11,467 --> 01:11:13,594
He's earning Rs.6,500
every month.

1052
01:11:13,802 --> 01:11:16,100
Why're you refusing this proposal?
- He's right, isn't he?

1053
01:11:16,305 --> 01:11:19,433
He's signing for Rs.6,500 and
taking Rs.10,000 as bribe.

1054
01:11:19,642 --> 01:11:20,267
What're you saying?

1055
01:11:20,476 --> 01:11:24,776
l'm not interested in a
boy who takes bribes.

1056
01:11:27,249 --> 01:11:32,448
Excuse me. l've come to know from uncle
that the groom takes bribes.

1057
01:11:32,755 --> 01:11:34,279
This is an honest and straight
forward family.

1058
01:11:34,490 --> 01:11:37,550
You leave the place, it'll not suit you.
- ls this the respectful way?

1059
01:11:37,993 --> 01:11:39,119
Then, l'll do one thing.

1060
01:11:39,328 --> 01:11:43,628
l'll pack some crisps and
chutney for you. Go away.

1061
01:11:43,832 --> 01:11:44,560
Hey Tuft!

1062
01:11:44,767 --> 01:11:45,893
Are you calling me tuft?

1063
01:11:46,168 --> 01:11:48,796
lf l tie this tuft,
it's personality.

1064
01:11:49,171 --> 01:11:51,401
lf l untie, it's university.

1065
01:11:51,774 --> 01:11:55,141
lf l show my character,
it's municipality.

1066
01:11:55,344 --> 01:11:59,644
Shall l tie, untie or show you?
Tell me. - Son-in-law.

1067
01:11:59,848 --> 01:12:01,816
You can leave...go...go.

1068
01:12:02,351 --> 01:12:04,979
What happened? - My father has
refused the proposal.

1069
01:12:05,187 --> 01:12:07,155
Saved me from creating trouble,
okay, l'll go now.

1070
01:12:07,790 --> 01:12:09,655
Why did he refuse the proposal?

1071
01:12:09,925 --> 01:12:11,324
lt seems the bridegroom
takes bribes.

1072
01:12:11,794 --> 01:12:14,422
My father has come to know about it.
So, he rejected him.

1073
01:12:16,598 --> 01:12:17,326
What was that noise?

1074
01:12:18,701 --> 01:12:19,326
Nothing.

1075
01:12:19,535 --> 01:12:20,661
Police quarters.

1076
01:12:21,870 --> 01:12:22,336
Sister!

1077
01:12:22,871 --> 01:12:24,566
Hey chili powder?
How come you're here?

1078
01:12:25,207 --> 01:12:26,174
Give me his house keys.

1079
01:12:26,375 --> 01:12:28,104
Why're you asking DC's
house keys?

1080
01:12:28,310 --> 01:12:30,778
He's always eating in Hotels.

1081
01:12:31,380 --> 01:12:33,348
So, l've come to cook for him.

1082
01:12:33,816 --> 01:12:35,181
l've asked him to come
home for lunch.

1083
01:12:35,384 --> 01:12:35,941
Oh!

1084
01:12:36,151 --> 01:12:38,915
ls it dress rehearsal before marriage?
Restrict it to cooking only.

1085
01:12:39,722 --> 01:12:40,780
What is his favourite food?

1086
01:12:40,989 --> 01:12:44,015
Except a flying plane & a floating ship,
he'll eat everything.

1087
01:12:47,429 --> 01:12:48,726
Sir, they're adulterating petrol
in the gas station.

1088
01:12:48,931 --> 01:12:50,728
Adulteration is in everything.
Go & complain to the Consumer court.

1089
01:12:50,933 --> 01:12:52,400
Sir, they've attacked a woman.
- What're you saying?

1090
01:12:52,601 --> 01:12:54,398
Look there, sir.
- What happened?

1091
01:12:54,603 --> 01:12:55,900
When l complained about the shortage
of petrol he supplied.

1092
01:12:56,105 --> 01:12:58,005
They kicked my scooter
and pushed me down.

1093
01:12:58,207 --> 01:13:00,402
What're you looking at?
First take her to a hospital. Go...go.

1094
01:13:00,609 --> 01:13:01,234
l don't want all that.

1095
01:13:01,443 --> 01:13:03,741
l'll not budge till l find a way out
for this problem. - What's this?

1096
01:13:08,884 --> 01:13:11,182
How much sir! - One litre.

1097
01:13:15,224 --> 01:13:16,350
We'll not supply in bottles.

1098
01:13:18,894 --> 01:13:19,519
Come on.

1099
01:13:39,581 --> 01:13:40,377
ls it one litre?

1100
01:13:42,351 --> 01:13:43,545
Sir, why did you beat him?

1101
01:13:43,752 --> 01:13:46,550
Who beat that woman?
Tell me...tell me.

1102
01:13:46,755 --> 01:13:47,221
Why're you beating him, sir?

1103
01:13:47,423 --> 01:13:49,721
How dare you beat a woman?

1104
01:13:49,925 --> 01:13:53,383
Sir, why're you beating us?
- Tell me, who beat that woman?

1105
01:13:53,595 --> 01:13:57,053
You don't have any right to ask us.
This is Annachi's petrol station. - Go away.

1106
01:13:57,266 --> 01:13:58,733
Are you giving 3/4 litre
for one litre?

1107
01:13:58,934 --> 01:14:00,561
There's another department
to enquire all this.

1108
01:14:00,769 --> 01:14:02,236
Anyone can enquire about
your short supply.

1109
01:14:02,438 --> 01:14:04,406
Any department can ask you.

1110
01:14:04,606 --> 01:14:06,233
Sir, this man had kicked me.

1111
01:14:08,444 --> 01:14:11,072
Sir, don't beat me.
- Where're you running away?

1112
01:14:11,280 --> 01:14:12,076
Do you think there's no one
to question you?

1113
01:14:12,281 --> 01:14:13,248
Get everyone into the jeep.

1114
01:14:15,784 --> 01:14:16,910
Close the petrol station
and seal it.

1115
01:14:17,786 --> 01:14:20,346
Annachi, DC has sealed
our petrol station.

1116
01:15:13,175 --> 01:15:14,904
Greetings sir.
- Where's your D.C.?

1117
01:15:15,110 --> 01:15:16,134
He has gone home for lunch.

1118
01:15:18,847 --> 01:15:21,475
Brother Paramasivan saide that you like
non-vegetarian food very much.

1119
01:15:21,850 --> 01:15:23,647
l don't know to cook
non-vegetarian. Sorry.

1120
01:15:24,186 --> 01:15:26,814
But, l'll learn to cook
non-vegetarian after marriage.

1121
01:15:27,022 --> 01:15:27,647
Hey Chili Powder!

1122
01:15:28,357 --> 01:15:30,917
Ever since l fell in love with you,
l've reduced taking non-vegetarian.

1123
01:15:31,126 --> 01:15:32,991
l'll stop it completely after marriage.

1124
01:15:34,029 --> 01:15:35,997
Great! Fantastic!

1125
01:15:44,873 --> 01:15:47,671
Do you know what my friends say?
l'm very lucky. - Why?

1126
01:15:48,043 --> 01:15:49,271
lt seems you're
straight forward.

1127
01:15:49,711 --> 01:15:52,009
And earned a good name
from all quaters. - ls it?

1128
01:15:52,714 --> 01:15:54,511
There's only one thing which
l don't like in you.

1129
01:15:55,551 --> 01:15:57,348
That one gray hair
in your moustache.

1130
01:15:57,553 --> 01:16:00,681
Shall l remove it?
- No...my lucky hair.

1131
01:16:00,989 --> 01:16:03,355
l'll remove it one day.
- Let me see.

1132
01:16:23,745 --> 01:16:25,212
You please sit down. - Okay.

1133
01:16:30,352 --> 01:16:31,148
l say, wait.

1134
01:16:32,087 --> 01:16:32,849
Who's that?

1135
01:16:35,090 --> 01:16:36,216
Are you married?

1136
01:16:36,758 --> 01:16:37,884
Who's this girl?

1137
01:16:39,027 --> 01:16:40,392
Are you having intimate relations with girls?

1138
01:16:41,597 --> 01:16:42,894
Do whatever you feel like doing?

1139
01:16:43,098 --> 01:16:44,895
Why're you troubling me?

1140
01:16:46,768 --> 01:16:49,566
Are you sealing my
petrol station?

1141
01:16:51,106 --> 01:16:55,566
ls it the way to show your loyalty
towards the millions l paid you?

1142
01:16:58,780 --> 01:17:01,578
Even the food that's sticking
in your hand.

1143
01:17:01,783 --> 01:17:04,752
Was bought by the money
l gave you as alms.

1144
01:17:07,456 --> 01:17:14,089
lf l don't like anyone l'll kill
him even if he's my sibling.

1145
01:17:14,796 --> 01:17:17,856
By staying with me, are you trying
to go against me?

1146
01:17:19,134 --> 01:17:23,594
l'm a man who will burn an
entire place to kill one man.

1147
01:17:24,139 --> 01:17:26,607
lf you go against me next time.

1148
01:17:26,808 --> 01:17:28,435
No one can find even the place
where you were killed.

1149
01:17:28,644 --> 01:17:30,271
Or find any clue
about your grave.

1150
01:17:30,479 --> 01:17:32,709
l'll shred you into pieces.

1151
01:17:35,150 --> 01:17:36,947
We'll go...go.

1152
01:17:43,825 --> 01:17:46,623
Please listen to me.

1153
01:17:46,828 --> 01:17:49,126
Wait...do you know what they had done?

1154
01:17:49,331 --> 01:17:50,628
Without knowing the truth...

1155
01:17:51,099 --> 01:17:53,624
l thought you were a good man.
- Please listen to me.

1156
01:17:55,337 --> 01:17:55,962
Leave me.

1157
01:17:56,505 --> 01:17:57,972
Don't go away in haste.

1158
01:18:24,599 --> 01:18:25,725
Annachi, petrol bunk is opened.

1159
01:18:25,934 --> 01:18:28,562
Hey, is it a finance company
to open & close frequently?

1160
01:18:28,770 --> 01:18:29,896
The insult which
we've faced, is history.

1161
01:18:30,105 --> 01:18:31,902
The day he entered our house
we should've taught him a lesson.

1162
01:18:32,174 --> 01:18:33,766
What do you want me to do?
Tell me, Annachi....

1163
01:18:34,109 --> 01:18:36,737
As a woman got hurt,
he got angry.

1164
01:18:37,112 --> 01:18:39,080
We asked many times...
but, he didn't reply.even once...

1165
01:18:40,282 --> 01:18:41,579
Hey, forget about it.

1166
01:18:42,184 --> 01:18:45,483
Hey, this news shouldn't be
published in evening's newspaper.

1167
01:18:52,627 --> 01:18:54,595
Bhuvana.... - Don't touch me.

1168
01:18:55,297 --> 01:18:56,924
Listen to me...
- What's left to say?

1169
01:18:57,132 --> 01:18:58,724
What happened was....
- lt's enough.

1170
01:18:59,301 --> 01:19:02,099
The faith which l had on you is lost.

1171
01:19:02,637 --> 01:19:06,095
God won't forgive you
for deceiving a girl.

1172
01:19:06,308 --> 01:19:07,605
Bhuvana, don't talk like a fool.

1173
01:19:07,809 --> 01:19:09,936
l'm a fool to have believed a cheat
who cheats the town.

1174
01:19:10,312 --> 01:19:12,109
Today, you used your position
and took money.

1175
01:19:12,314 --> 01:19:14,748
Tomorrow, what's the guarantee that
you won't sell me? - Hey, stop it...

1176
01:19:17,486 --> 01:19:19,147
l can just leave you & go away.

1177
01:19:19,521 --> 01:19:21,421
But, you'll commit suicide
within a week.

1178
01:19:22,491 --> 01:19:23,458
l can't bear that....

1179
01:19:23,825 --> 01:19:26,055
Do you know why l took bribe?

1180
01:19:27,329 --> 01:19:29,957
Every police man's job
has become commercial.

1181
01:19:30,332 --> 01:19:33,301
But, l consider this uniform
as my honour.

1182
01:19:33,502 --> 01:19:35,970
My father considered his
job as sacred.

1183
01:19:36,671 --> 01:19:39,970
Whichever caste or religion a person
may belong to, if mistake is committed,

1184
01:19:40,342 --> 01:19:43,311
Only police has the right to get it rectified.

1185
01:19:43,845 --> 01:19:46,814
That's why, l educated my son &
asked him to take up police job.

1186
01:19:47,015 --> 01:19:49,643
Then, will Saamy become
lnspector in our place?

1187
01:19:49,851 --> 01:19:51,409
Why're you asking like
a competitor?

1188
01:19:51,853 --> 01:19:54,822
lf my son gets a job....He'll become
an officer, in this place.

1189
01:19:58,360 --> 01:20:01,818
Saamy, you've got an interview card.

1190
01:20:03,532 --> 01:20:24,546
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

1191
01:20:25,887 --> 01:20:29,152
Oh Margosa tree, Tamarind tree
Banyan tree, Holy Fig tree,

1192
01:20:29,357 --> 01:20:31,985
l'm going to leave the village.

1193
01:20:33,028 --> 01:20:36,327
Oh Sengamalam! Who comes &
takes bath in the river.

1194
01:20:36,531 --> 01:20:38,999
l'm going to leave the village.

1195
01:20:40,035 --> 01:20:43,334
l'm going to a far away place
where factory siren can't be heard.

1196
01:20:43,705 --> 01:20:47,004
l'm going to a far away place
which the sparrow hasn't seen.

1197
01:20:47,242 --> 01:20:53,511
l'm going to leave the village
wearing police uniform.

1198
01:20:54,549 --> 01:21:01,011
He's going to leave the village
wearing police uniform.

1199
01:21:18,607 --> 01:21:47,131
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

1200
01:21:47,936 --> 01:21:51,064
After waking up in the morning...

1201
01:21:51,439 --> 01:21:54,408
l'll play brandish sticks.

1202
01:21:54,943 --> 01:21:58,401
lf l get hurt by playing
brandish sticks,

1203
01:21:58,613 --> 01:22:01,411
l'll apply the soil of my mother land on it.

1204
01:22:05,487 --> 01:22:08,422
My desire is fulfilled.

1205
01:22:08,957 --> 01:22:11,926
My father's heart is
filled with joy.

1206
01:22:12,627 --> 01:22:19,089
l'm going to ride a bike
happily at a high speed.

1207
01:22:19,968 --> 01:22:26,601
When Aruasaamy will come in a procession
landlord will give respect to him.

1208
01:22:27,142 --> 01:22:33,775
When Saamy sees the young girls
he'll fold his hands.

1209
01:22:58,707 --> 01:23:20,222
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

1210
01:23:20,562 --> 01:23:23,656
Oh Dear....Oh dear...

1211
01:23:23,898 --> 01:23:25,331
Oh dear...Where're you going?

1212
01:23:25,533 --> 01:23:27,160
Oh dear...Oh dear...

1213
01:23:31,373 --> 01:23:44,514
Oh train...Oh train...

1214
01:23:45,220 --> 01:23:48,018
Those who print fake currencies,

1215
01:23:48,723 --> 01:23:51,851
Those who charge high interest rates,

1216
01:23:52,227 --> 01:23:55,526
Those who steal hens...and goats...

1217
01:23:55,730 --> 01:23:58,699
Better reform yourselves
within six months.

1218
01:24:02,937 --> 01:24:06,031
lf you keep concubine
l'll not spare you.

1219
01:24:06,408 --> 01:24:09,377
l'll smash those who
abuse their parents.

1220
01:24:10,078 --> 01:24:13,536
lf l see the boys playing
with marbles,catapults,

1221
01:24:13,748 --> 01:24:16,717
l'll join them happily.

1222
01:24:17,419 --> 01:24:24,052
He'll punish those who
commit mistakes.

1223
01:24:24,426 --> 01:24:27,725
And if those people realise
their mistakes.

1224
01:24:27,929 --> 01:24:31,558
l swear, l don't want anything else
from them.

1225
01:25:27,889 --> 01:25:30,187
Son, how did your interview go?

1226
01:25:31,559 --> 01:25:33,026
Father, this job won't
be suitable for me.

1227
01:25:33,228 --> 01:25:34,024
What do you mean?

1228
01:25:35,396 --> 01:25:36,363
l don't want it...
- Why?

1229
01:25:37,232 --> 01:25:38,859
Didn't you reply properly?

1230
01:25:40,235 --> 01:25:41,532
l would've replied
if they had questioned me.

1231
01:25:41,836 --> 01:25:45,294
But they want bribe....
l Don't want it father.

1232
01:25:46,908 --> 01:25:50,036
You want the job but
you're hesitating.

1233
01:25:51,246 --> 01:25:54,545
How much they asked?
- 7 Lakhs, father.

1234
01:25:59,754 --> 01:26:00,618
Father, what's all this?

1235
01:26:00,922 --> 01:26:03,982
l sold our fields for 5 lakhs.

1236
01:26:04,359 --> 01:26:06,054
l've pledged the house for 2 lakhs.

1237
01:26:06,761 --> 01:26:07,659
By selling the fields...

1238
01:26:08,196 --> 01:26:10,164
Son, to get something
we've to lose something.

1239
01:26:11,432 --> 01:26:15,892
30 years ago, l exercised & conditioned
my body to become a policeman.

1240
01:26:16,604 --> 01:26:19,300
As my father was unable
to give a mere Rs.8000,

1241
01:26:19,707 --> 01:26:21,140
l was unable to get
that job.

1242
01:26:22,210 --> 01:26:25,407
On the first day when
l worked in the fields.

1243
01:26:25,613 --> 01:26:28,081
l can't express the anguish
which l went through.

1244
01:26:28,950 --> 01:26:30,315
You shouldn't face
similar situation.

1245
01:26:31,286 --> 01:26:32,082
You should get that job.

1246
01:26:32,954 --> 01:26:34,751
l started my work sincerely
in the office.

1247
01:26:35,390 --> 01:26:37,915
But it's feed back was....
Politicians problems...

1248
01:26:38,226 --> 01:26:39,591
l got a bad name
among higher officials.

1249
01:26:39,794 --> 01:26:40,761
l got transferred frequently.

1250
01:26:41,629 --> 01:26:43,256
Atlast, they transferred
me to Trichy.

1251
01:26:44,799 --> 01:26:45,424
What's this, man?

1252
01:26:46,467 --> 01:26:48,435
You've joined very recently and you're
refusing to accept bribe from us!

1253
01:26:48,970 --> 01:26:50,597
You must've got this job
by giving bribe.

1254
01:26:50,972 --> 01:26:51,939
When are you going to get that money back?

1255
01:26:52,307 --> 01:26:55,105
You take as much as you want &
don't bother about it.

1256
01:26:58,146 --> 01:26:58,612
Sorry sir.

1257
01:27:00,148 --> 01:27:03,606
You should stop illicit liquor trade
rowdism & vandalism.

1258
01:27:04,652 --> 01:27:06,051
Or else, l've to do my duty.

1259
01:27:08,489 --> 01:27:10,116
You should've given them,
saying ''Pattu has given it''.

1260
01:27:10,325 --> 01:27:12,725
l told them. But they've the
support of the new DCP.

1261
01:28:17,158 --> 01:28:18,455
Can you pound without a pestle?

1262
01:28:19,494 --> 01:28:22,190
Can you be in politics without rowdism?
You can't, isn't it?

1263
01:28:22,563 --> 01:28:25,691
Then, why've you arrested him?
Release him.

1264
01:28:26,067 --> 01:28:27,034
Do you've bail order?

1265
01:28:27,235 --> 01:28:29,203
You're a policeman, right?
Don't you know?

1266
01:28:29,504 --> 01:28:31,267
Today is Sunday. Can a bail order be got today?

1267
01:28:31,572 --> 01:28:32,869
l'll get it tomorrow
release him now.

1268
01:28:34,676 --> 01:28:38,237
FlR is registered. l can't release him
without bail order.

1269
01:28:38,446 --> 01:28:40,209
FlR! Tear it
& throw it away.

1270
01:28:44,519 --> 01:28:45,486
Beat him & lock him inside.

1271
01:28:47,021 --> 01:28:48,318
Did you hit our ward officer?

1272
01:28:48,523 --> 01:28:50,150
lf l hit him, He'll turn into pulp.

1273
01:28:50,358 --> 01:28:51,985
Why did you hit him?

1274
01:28:52,193 --> 01:28:54,320
Hey, as you've come in uniform,
you've saved your skin.

1275
01:28:54,529 --> 01:28:56,156
Or else, l would've bashed you nicely.

1276
01:28:57,031 --> 01:28:58,430
We should immediately transfer him.

1277
01:28:58,866 --> 01:28:59,833
Transfer, won't be enough.

1278
01:29:00,535 --> 01:29:02,162
Like branding the cows coming for sale,

1279
01:29:02,370 --> 01:29:04,497
We should
confine him to his house, without hitting him.

1280
01:29:05,206 --> 01:29:08,733
We should teach him that politicians
are born criminals.

1281
01:29:21,089 --> 01:29:21,885
We're from vigilance department.

1282
01:29:22,090 --> 01:29:23,887
We've got the information that
you've taken bribe.

1283
01:29:24,425 --> 01:29:25,722
We've to check your jeep.

1284
01:29:26,094 --> 01:29:30,724
For my sincerity...They suspended me
accusing me of taking bribe.

1285
01:29:31,599 --> 01:29:32,725
You should definitely attend the
marriage with your family.

1286
01:29:32,934 --> 01:29:34,231
Will l fail to attend
Saamy's marriage?

1287
01:29:34,435 --> 01:29:36,232
lt seems, our kinsman is coming.

1288
01:29:37,605 --> 01:29:39,835
Welcome kinsman....
- Come here....

1289
01:29:40,041 --> 01:29:40,564
What's it?

1290
01:29:41,609 --> 01:29:42,906
First stop distributing
the invitations.

1291
01:29:43,111 --> 01:29:44,738
This marriage won't be performed
- What do you mean?

1292
01:29:44,946 --> 01:29:48,746
Your son has been arrested for
taking bribe in a prostitution case.

1293
01:29:48,950 --> 01:29:50,076
Don't cast wrong aspersions.

1294
01:29:50,284 --> 01:29:51,911
Hey, who hasn't taken bribe
in the country?

1295
01:29:52,120 --> 01:29:55,089
No fool will take bribe & get his name
published in the paper.

1296
01:29:55,790 --> 01:29:57,587
No. This marriage won't be performed.
You stop this marriage.

1297
01:30:07,135 --> 01:30:07,601
Father...

1298
01:30:10,972 --> 01:30:12,098
Do you also believe it?

1299
01:30:13,975 --> 01:30:16,500
l won't believe even if
Lord Muruga comes & says.

1300
01:30:17,812 --> 01:30:19,609
You won't do a wrong thing.

1301
01:30:20,148 --> 01:30:25,780
Our village people say that you
want to multiply 7 lakhs into 70 lakhs.

1302
01:30:26,421 --> 01:30:27,115
Let them talk.

1303
01:30:27,422 --> 01:30:30,448
This's the punishment
for being honest.

1304
01:30:30,992 --> 01:30:32,289
Justice & law are dead.

1305
01:30:33,094 --> 01:30:34,959
What did law do to you,
for being honest?

1306
01:30:35,496 --> 01:30:37,191
lt suspended you & made you
to stay in the house.

1307
01:30:37,498 --> 01:30:40,126
Being brave is not enough,
you should be intelligent also.

1308
01:30:40,768 --> 01:30:42,963
Without taking bribe....
They accused you of taking bribe.

1309
01:30:43,337 --> 01:30:44,861
Hereafter, you take bribe
& do good things.

1310
01:30:45,173 --> 01:30:46,640
You create a law for yourself.

1311
01:30:47,775 --> 01:30:49,402
There may be 100's of
bad people in a place.

1312
01:30:49,677 --> 01:30:50,302
Forget about them.

1313
01:30:50,812 --> 01:30:52,575
ln the same place there may
be four good people.

1314
01:30:52,780 --> 01:30:54,008
You do good to them.

1315
01:30:54,816 --> 01:30:56,807
ln Epic Ramayanam, if Vali was
a good person.

1316
01:30:57,018 --> 01:30:58,485
Raman would've hit him
facing him.

1317
01:30:58,686 --> 01:31:01,348
Since he was a bad persons
be hit him from behind.

1318
01:31:01,556 --> 01:31:03,114
According to the rules of
the war, it's a sin.

1319
01:31:03,524 --> 01:31:05,788
But, according to human law
it's right.

1320
01:31:06,627 --> 01:31:10,324
Saamy, l had lost 5 children
before you were born...

1321
01:31:10,765 --> 01:31:14,292
You're my 6th child. That's why
l named you Arusaamy.(Six Swamy)

1322
01:31:16,637 --> 01:31:20,164
You were born after
killing five children.

1323
01:31:20,441 --> 01:31:22,500
You do anything for good things.

1324
01:31:22,844 --> 01:31:24,243
You kill anyone.

1325
01:31:25,713 --> 01:31:29,205
Nothing wrong in that.
There's no sin in that.

1326
01:31:32,587 --> 01:31:37,490
l struggled for six months to prove
myself innocent in the court.

1327
01:31:38,159 --> 01:31:40,787
We can find Politicians & rich men
in all the places.

1328
01:31:41,229 --> 01:31:42,321
l can't reform all of them.

1329
01:31:42,530 --> 01:31:45,124
That's why, as my father had said,
l changed myself.

1330
01:31:45,500 --> 01:31:47,968
Or else, l wouldn't have stayed for
such a long time in this place.

1331
01:31:48,703 --> 01:31:51,297
Bhuvana, l didn't take bribe
from the public.

1332
01:31:51,906 --> 01:31:54,636
l took bribe from the evil persons
who deceive the Government.

1333
01:31:55,376 --> 01:31:58,368
Bribe, which l'm taking is like
offerings to God.

1334
01:31:58,980 --> 01:32:02,108
lt'll go to temple's trust
but not to God.

1335
01:32:03,184 --> 01:32:04,048
Believe me.

1336
01:32:10,424 --> 01:32:12,790
Hey, what's our caste & tradition.

1337
01:32:12,994 --> 01:32:14,359
We don't know who's he...

1338
01:32:14,562 --> 01:32:16,086
You've done such a mistake.

1339
01:32:16,297 --> 01:32:17,525
Mother, he's a good person.

1340
01:32:17,765 --> 01:32:20,962
What's your age? Why do
you think like this?

1341
01:32:21,235 --> 01:32:24,693
You call & talk to him... - Shut up.
That's why l wanted you,

1342
01:32:24,906 --> 01:32:27,898
to check whether your daughter is going
to college or somewhere else. - Silence.

1343
01:32:28,709 --> 01:32:29,641
At this vulnerable age of falling in love,

1344
01:32:29,844 --> 01:32:31,277
lt's your mistake to send her
to college.

1345
01:32:31,479 --> 01:32:33,879
Now, who'll take the responsibility?

1346
01:32:34,081 --> 01:32:36,641
You call & talk to him.
- What to talk?

1347
01:32:36,851 --> 01:32:38,250
At teenage, while she is going
to college,

1348
01:32:38,452 --> 01:32:41,250
lf you wish to marry her,
then, the family will be in problem.

1349
01:32:41,455 --> 01:32:43,423
Will you please shut up?

1350
01:32:45,126 --> 01:32:49,085
Look, she won't be reformed by
pouring water on her.

1351
01:32:49,297 --> 01:32:53,028
You call that boy & talk to him.
That'll be better.

1352
01:32:55,603 --> 01:32:56,763
You take coffee.

1353
01:32:58,673 --> 01:33:00,197
To dissolve the sugar you mix the coffee well.
Tumble the coffee well.

1354
01:33:00,408 --> 01:33:02,069
Only then, sugar will be dissolved.

1355
01:33:03,611 --> 01:33:05,772
lt may be Hot...Cool it
and drink.

1356
01:33:10,618 --> 01:33:12,984
Don't sip...Pour it in
your mouth.

1357
01:33:14,055 --> 01:33:16,922
They're giving such elaborate instructions
for drinking coffee. Very funny!

1358
01:33:17,792 --> 01:33:23,025
We can't even imagine that our
girl loves a police officer.

1359
01:33:23,230 --> 01:33:26,097
Grandma, it's wrong to love a thief.

1360
01:33:26,300 --> 01:33:27,824
We're different from you.

1361
01:33:28,135 --> 01:33:30,501
With what faith can we marry
our daughter to you?

1362
01:33:30,738 --> 01:33:33,798
Apart from being a good husband
and a good son-in-law,

1363
01:33:33,908 --> 01:33:36,077
l'll be your son...You believe my words &
get your daughter married to me.

1364
01:33:36,077 --> 01:33:38,910
She's a very young girl. Not even
finished her college.

1365
01:33:39,113 --> 01:33:40,944
Before that, how can we
perform her marriage?

1366
01:33:41,148 --> 01:33:45,050
Don't worry, l'll treat your daughter
as a child. l'll keep her happy.

1367
01:33:45,319 --> 01:33:49,187
lf we accept your proposal
how much dowry will you expect?

1368
01:33:49,390 --> 01:33:51,153
You give me one sovereign
of gold & Re.1 .

1369
01:33:51,359 --> 01:33:54,260
Rs.1 ...What's this?
He's asking like CM's salary.

1370
01:33:54,462 --> 01:33:57,363
Sir, do you consider us
beggars? - That's it.

1371
01:33:57,565 --> 01:33:59,863
My sons's monthly salary
is Rs.7000.

1372
01:34:00,067 --> 01:34:03,503
Our women earn Rs.10,000
monthly by packing spices.

1373
01:34:03,704 --> 01:34:05,695
Our son-in-law. - Why do you talk
about all that now? Forget it.

1374
01:34:05,906 --> 01:34:07,806
Let's talk about other things.
- Okay, let's forget it.

1375
01:34:08,009 --> 01:34:11,968
We'll offer you generously...
You ask unhesitatingly.

1376
01:34:12,179 --> 01:34:14,670
Then, you give one lakh &
100 sovereigns of Gold.

1377
01:34:14,882 --> 01:34:16,907
What's this? You're asking
in PM's range.

1378
01:34:17,418 --> 01:34:20,945
l don't want anything. You give me only
your daughter. That's enough.

1379
01:34:21,155 --> 01:34:23,146
l'm living for Bhuvana.

1380
01:34:23,357 --> 01:34:26,121
Till l'm alive, l want to
live for Bhuvana.

1381
01:34:26,560 --> 01:34:27,925
Bless me.

1382
01:34:28,129 --> 01:34:28,652
Hubby...

1383
01:34:29,764 --> 01:34:30,662
May you long live.

1384
01:34:32,266 --> 01:34:36,600
First son-in-law is a priest
& 2nd one is a policeman.

1385
01:34:36,837 --> 01:34:37,496
Grandpa...

1386
01:34:37,705 --> 01:34:40,674
What's it? Hubby...
- We like you very much.

1387
01:34:41,642 --> 01:34:42,904
l don't like this.

1388
01:34:48,049 --> 01:34:50,415
Your face shows that you're not happy.

1389
01:34:51,285 --> 01:34:53,412
Sir, l'll wait till you believe me
comprehensively.

1390
01:34:53,621 --> 01:34:56,419
Sir, you seem to be a good person.

1391
01:34:57,024 --> 01:35:00,016
But, l've about 400 relatives
in `Ambasamudhiram'.

1392
01:35:00,227 --> 01:35:02,388
l don't know what to
tell them. - Uncle.

1393
01:35:02,697 --> 01:35:05,097
You forget about 400 persons.
You select a good person.

1394
01:35:05,299 --> 01:35:08,860
Srinivasa, if l had a son & sought your
daughter's alliance, won't You accept?

1395
01:35:09,070 --> 01:35:11,766
l'm considering him as my son &
asking your daughter's hand.

1396
01:35:12,873 --> 01:35:16,070
That day, when l fell at your feet
you said, ''l'm like your father.''

1397
01:35:16,277 --> 01:35:18,108
l don't know what you meant by that.

1398
01:35:18,312 --> 01:35:21,110
But, l consider you as my son.

1399
01:35:23,150 --> 01:35:26,881
Why're you still thinking?
Say `yes'. - Okay.

1400
01:35:28,055 --> 01:35:31,024
ln the year of `Chitra Banu'
on Jan 4th...

1401
01:35:31,258 --> 01:35:35,126
Palani Sriram Chokka Lingam's son
Saamy(alias) Arusaamy.

1402
01:35:42,970 --> 01:35:56,441
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

1403
01:35:57,118 --> 01:36:01,612
ls this the one...

1404
01:36:01,822 --> 01:36:06,521
ls this the day which
l was expecting.

1405
01:36:06,727 --> 01:36:11,221
ls he the one.

1406
01:36:11,432 --> 01:36:16,665
ls he the groom,
who will garland me?

1407
01:36:16,871 --> 01:36:21,604
Now, my dreams are coming true...

1408
01:36:21,909 --> 01:36:26,369
But, l've become your partner.

1409
01:36:26,614 --> 01:36:35,318
The days which l count for the
marriage, are a pleasant burden...

1410
01:36:35,523 --> 01:36:40,085
Without separating the lips &
without raising the voice.

1411
01:36:40,294 --> 01:36:45,197
l'll sing a song for myself.

1412
01:37:04,552 --> 01:37:29,071
<i>TAMlLlNl</i>

1413
01:37:29,410 --> 01:37:38,842
Hereafter, the drama which we'll
play in the house will be pleasant.

1414
01:37:39,053 --> 01:37:47,518
Your eyes will search
me every where.

1415
01:37:48,062 --> 01:37:50,189
You'll find me near the stair case.

1416
01:37:50,397 --> 01:37:52,695
You'll act as though,
you haven't seen me.

1417
01:37:53,167 --> 01:37:55,135
You'll embrace me.

1418
01:37:55,336 --> 01:37:57,702
You'll hug me in the
middle of the stair case.

1419
01:37:58,239 --> 01:38:02,539
Fear will beget fear &
it'll vanish.

1420
01:38:02,910 --> 01:38:06,710
Shyness will feel shy &
vanish.

1421
01:39:22,323 --> 01:39:31,459
You'll prepare lunch by yourself
on Sunday afternoons.

1422
01:39:31,832 --> 01:39:40,467
You'll ask me to watch
the fun & wash my clothes.

1423
01:39:40,841 --> 01:39:43,139
The entire town is afraid of you.

1424
01:39:43,344 --> 01:39:45,642
But, you behave like a child with me.

1425
01:39:46,013 --> 01:39:47,981
l'll feel proud of me.

1426
01:39:48,182 --> 01:39:50,480
We both are made for each other!

1427
01:39:51,185 --> 01:39:54,985
My heart is drenched with happiness.

1428
01:39:55,356 --> 01:39:59,486
My world will blossom.

1429
01:40:49,576 --> 01:40:51,373
There's no inter-caste anomaly.

1430
01:40:51,578 --> 01:40:53,375
There's no inter-caste anomaly.

1431
01:40:53,747 --> 01:40:55,715
Sir, read `Konar Tamil'.

1432
01:40:55,916 --> 01:40:56,883
l ate at `Devar's mess.

1433
01:40:57,084 --> 01:40:58,051
l had tea in a `Nair's shop'.

1434
01:40:58,252 --> 01:40:59,378
l bought provisions
from Nadar's shop.

1435
01:40:59,586 --> 01:41:00,883
l borrowed money from
chettiar's house.

1436
01:41:01,088 --> 01:41:03,113
Sir, how can we believe that
there's no caste system .

1437
01:41:04,258 --> 01:41:05,987
Wow, he has put me in a fix.

1438
01:41:06,193 --> 01:41:07,888
Sir...Greetings sir...

1439
01:41:08,095 --> 01:41:08,720
What do you want, man?

1440
01:41:08,929 --> 01:41:12,330
My son is a good student.
but they aren't admitting him in the school.

1441
01:41:12,599 --> 01:41:13,896
Aren't they?

1442
01:41:14,268 --> 01:41:15,895
Sir, greetings... - Greetings.

1443
01:41:16,103 --> 01:41:18,071
This boy is from a poor family
but studies well.

1444
01:41:18,272 --> 01:41:19,068
Give him a seat.

1445
01:41:19,273 --> 01:41:21,070
l can't give him admission in
a convent school. - Why?

1446
01:41:21,275 --> 01:41:22,173
His parents are uneducated.

1447
01:41:22,376 --> 01:41:24,469
Then, do one thing.
First give admission to the parents.

1448
01:41:24,711 --> 01:41:26,906
Let them obtain their degrees.
Then admit him.

1449
01:41:27,114 --> 01:41:28,741
Priest what're you blabbering?

1450
01:41:28,949 --> 01:41:29,574
l'm not blabbering, this child
is going to study.

1451
01:41:29,783 --> 01:41:31,080
His parent's age is around 40.

1452
01:41:31,285 --> 01:41:32,343
How will they study now?

1453
01:41:32,553 --> 01:41:34,680
lf parents are educated, only then
they can teach their children.

1454
01:41:34,888 --> 01:41:38,085
Then, why're you here working as
a teacher? - Come here.

1455
01:41:38,292 --> 01:41:40,419
What's it? - Here, you've to give
donation to get admission.

1456
01:41:40,627 --> 01:41:42,595
Okay, you get it from
those who have.

1457
01:41:42,796 --> 01:41:45,264
He's poor, but he studies well...
Give him a seat.

1458
01:41:45,466 --> 01:41:46,933
What is he going to
do after studying?

1459
01:41:47,468 --> 01:41:49,936
Children's education will uplift lndia.

1460
01:41:50,137 --> 01:41:52,367
So said by Dr.Abdul Kalam whose
photo you've hung on the wall.

1461
01:41:52,573 --> 01:41:54,438
And you're refusing to give education
to a poor student.

1462
01:41:54,641 --> 01:41:55,608
ls it not injustice?

1463
01:41:55,809 --> 01:41:58,334
They all belongs to
cloth less caste.

1464
01:41:58,745 --> 01:42:01,612
So, clothes is the criteria, isn't it?.
- Yes.

1465
01:42:01,815 --> 01:42:03,442
l'll solve it now itself.

1466
01:42:09,156 --> 01:42:10,623
Hands up, boy...

1467
01:42:10,824 --> 01:42:12,291
Why does a chair need a cloth?

1468
01:42:12,493 --> 01:42:14,222
You need a shirt.

1469
01:42:15,996 --> 01:42:17,964
He has a shirt.
Give him a seat now.

1470
01:42:18,165 --> 01:42:20,963
ls shirt alone enough?
- Then, do you want pant also?

1471
01:42:21,168 --> 01:42:23,636
ls this okay for a pant?
- Oh God...l'll give him a seat.

1472
01:42:25,339 --> 01:42:25,805
Take him.

1473
01:42:26,173 --> 01:42:28,141
Sir, did my son get admission?

1474
01:42:28,342 --> 01:42:30,310
He got a seat & shirt also.

1475
01:42:30,511 --> 01:42:31,637
How did you wangle it?

1476
01:42:32,513 --> 01:42:33,912
l told the truth.

1477
01:42:35,516 --> 01:42:37,313
On January 12th,

1478
01:42:37,518 --> 01:42:40,817
The opposition party badmouthed
the ruling party leader.

1479
01:42:41,021 --> 01:42:44,980
So, the ruling party has decided to go
for one day's strike in the city.

1480
01:42:45,192 --> 01:42:50,824
Hey, it's a bandh of our party.
No one should come out.

1481
01:42:51,198 --> 01:42:53,325
Even tea or petty shops
shouldn't open.

1482
01:42:53,534 --> 01:42:55,832
lnform our henchmen in
all the areas. - Yes boss.

1483
01:42:56,203 --> 01:42:58,330
Sir, if there's bandh before `Pongal' fetival?
How will it be?

1484
01:42:58,872 --> 01:43:01,170
lt's a bandh called by the ruling party
so, close all your shops.

1485
01:43:01,375 --> 01:43:03,843
Government is not supporting it.
lt's ruling party's Bandh.

1486
01:43:04,044 --> 01:43:06,672
These are all perishable goods
we can't store them.

1487
01:43:06,880 --> 01:43:10,839
We've bought goods
on high interest rates.

1488
01:43:11,051 --> 01:43:12,348
Sir, if you insist like this
what can we do?

1489
01:43:12,886 --> 01:43:15,514
lf we close our shops,
business will suffer a great loss.

1490
01:43:15,722 --> 01:43:18,691
Okay, you all sign on a paper
demanding protection.

1491
01:43:18,892 --> 01:43:20,860
l'll see to rest of the things.
- Thank you very much, sir.

1492
01:43:22,563 --> 01:43:24,793
Sir Annachi is involved
in this affair.

1493
01:43:25,065 --> 01:43:26,191
Do we've to interfere in this?

1494
01:43:26,400 --> 01:43:29,528
All hard workers are
suffering a lot.

1495
01:43:29,903 --> 01:43:31,200
Forget about that man...

1496
01:43:38,579 --> 01:43:40,206
Sir, who's on duty in Palayamkottai?
- Kumarasamy.

1497
01:43:40,414 --> 01:43:42,211
Whoever creates problem,
put him in jail. - Okay sir.

1498
01:43:48,589 --> 01:43:50,887
We learnt about today's Bandh
only from the newspaper.

1499
01:43:56,263 --> 01:43:58,891
Sir, as you had said, l've given
security to the entire state.

1500
01:43:59,099 --> 01:44:00,726
Not only here, there won't be
any problem at any place.

1501
01:44:08,775 --> 01:44:11,073
Police chases & beats the rowdies.

1502
01:44:11,278 --> 01:44:13,746
Till Saamy sir is there,
l can bravely open the shop.

1503
01:44:23,123 --> 01:44:24,920
Thank you, sir... Long live, sir...

1504
01:44:42,909 --> 01:44:46,606
Hello, who's it? Annachi has gone out.

1505
01:44:47,147 --> 01:44:48,774
Put down your phone..

1506
01:44:49,149 --> 01:44:51,549
Saamy is not a human being.
Truly, he's a God.

1507
01:44:51,752 --> 01:44:52,514
Very good, Paramasivam...

1508
01:44:52,719 --> 01:44:54,448
You're protecting the Public
against ruling Party's bandh.

1509
01:44:54,655 --> 01:44:55,622
Whether it's ruling
or opposition Party.

1510
01:44:55,822 --> 01:44:56,789
l'll give importance to the Public.

1511
01:44:57,157 --> 01:44:59,455
lf he wasn't there, we couldn't
have run the business.

1512
01:44:59,660 --> 01:45:02,629
They've won & we've lost.

1513
01:45:02,829 --> 01:45:05,389
Bandh announced by ruling Party
passed off peacefully.

1514
01:45:05,832 --> 01:45:08,960
Except in Tirunelveli, there was no
disturbance in daily routines.

1515
01:45:09,169 --> 01:45:12,730
All the shops were open.
There were no untoward incidents.

1516
01:45:12,939 --> 01:45:14,634
Start the car.

1517
01:45:14,841 --> 01:45:17,469
Annachi, don't be in a hurry.
Everything is over.

1518
01:45:17,678 --> 01:45:18,474
Now, if you hit him...

1519
01:45:18,679 --> 01:45:20,306
He's a cheat. l didn't refer to him.

1520
01:45:21,181 --> 01:45:24,480
How dare businessmen
open their shops?

1521
01:45:24,685 --> 01:45:26,482
lt's all because of
that Saamy's support.

1522
01:45:26,687 --> 01:45:28,985
They know what'll happen if
they act against Annachi.

1523
01:45:29,189 --> 01:45:31,657
Annachi, coming Friday,
Saamy is going to get married.

1524
01:45:32,025 --> 01:45:34,152
At that time, all Police men will
be in the marriage hall.

1525
01:45:34,528 --> 01:45:36,996
On that day, let's show the
businessmen our true colour.

1526
01:45:37,197 --> 01:45:39,165
Their corpses should be
telecast in the T.V.

1527
01:45:40,367 --> 01:45:42,164
On Bogi festival, people burn all the rubbish,

1528
01:45:42,369 --> 01:45:46,169
And create pollution generating
Carbon-monoxide & dioxide.

1529
01:45:46,373 --> 01:45:48,841
People have already created a hole
in the Ozone layer.

1530
01:45:49,042 --> 01:45:51,010
Don't know where they are going
to create more holes.

1531
01:45:51,378 --> 01:45:53,346
Aunt, stop.

1532
01:45:53,714 --> 01:45:55,181
lt seems Uncle sleeps on this mat.

1533
01:45:55,382 --> 01:45:56,508
Are you going to put it in the fire?

1534
01:45:56,717 --> 01:45:58,116
lt has become old.
- Do you mean Uncle?

1535
01:45:58,385 --> 01:45:58,851
Shut up!

1536
01:45:59,052 --> 01:46:01,850
lf you give it to people who don't
have mat, they can sleep on it. Give it to me.

1537
01:46:02,089 --> 01:46:04,057
Shut up & get lost.

1538
01:46:04,224 --> 01:46:06,692
Uncle, please stop. What're you
putting in the fire.

1539
01:46:06,893 --> 01:46:07,689
Old clothes.

1540
01:46:07,894 --> 01:46:09,953
They may be old for you,
but they're new for them.

1541
01:46:10,163 --> 01:46:12,688
lf you give them they'll wear them.
- lt's good to burn old things.

1542
01:46:13,066 --> 01:46:15,534
The proverb says ''Discard old things &
accept the new ones''.

1543
01:46:16,002 --> 01:46:17,196
That is what Bogi festival is for, isn't it?

1544
01:46:18,405 --> 01:46:21,636
So, anything which is old can
be put in the fire, isn't it? - Sure.

1545
01:46:25,912 --> 01:46:27,209
Hey, what're you doing?

1546
01:46:27,414 --> 01:46:29,882
This is the oldest thing
in the entire District.

1547
01:46:30,083 --> 01:46:31,710
l'm going to put this in the fire.

1548
01:46:32,085 --> 01:46:33,552
And enjoy Bogi festival.

1549
01:46:34,755 --> 01:46:36,723
Hey, don't harm him. - Why?

1550
01:46:36,923 --> 01:46:37,719
He's my brother.

1551
01:46:37,924 --> 01:46:39,653
Let him be your brother or anyone.

1552
01:46:39,860 --> 01:46:41,885
First keep the clothes down.

1553
01:46:42,262 --> 01:46:44,890
Only then, l won't put him
in the fire. - Get lost.

1554
01:46:45,265 --> 01:46:46,027
Children, take the clothes.

1555
01:46:48,602 --> 01:46:51,730
Thanks Uncle.
- l used you for a good cause.

1556
01:46:52,105 --> 01:46:54,164
Don't be afraid. l won't put you
in the fire.

1557
01:46:54,374 --> 01:46:58,071
Come. Let's go to your house &
have a cup of coffee. come..

1558
01:46:58,712 --> 01:46:59,736
Open your eyes.

1559
01:47:02,282 --> 01:47:05,843
Hey, it's been 2 days since he died.

1560
01:47:06,052 --> 01:47:08,680
And you're celebrating
Bogi festival!

1561
01:47:09,055 --> 01:47:10,750
You shouldn't celebrate
even Pongal festival which comes later..

1562
01:47:17,130 --> 01:47:17,755
Stop it!

1563
01:47:18,131 --> 01:47:20,031
How long will you be playing
the same music?

1564
01:47:20,233 --> 01:47:23,259
Beat the drum in the modern trend.

1565
01:47:26,473 --> 01:47:29,704
Come.. come.. You must eat & go.

1566
01:47:29,910 --> 01:47:30,774
My stomach is upset.

1567
01:47:30,977 --> 01:47:33,275
Then, eat & discard your waste
in a corner.

1568
01:47:33,480 --> 01:47:35,778
Stupid! Doesn't know what to
talk in a marriage.

1569
01:47:47,994 --> 01:47:49,621
Hey, leave me... leave me..

1570
01:48:01,842 --> 01:48:03,639
Hey, why're you doing like this?

1571
01:48:03,844 --> 01:48:05,471
How dare you defy our boss &
open the shop?

1572
01:48:40,080 --> 01:48:41,047
Beat the drum.

1573
01:48:46,753 --> 01:48:49,881
Sir.. sir..

1574
01:48:50,257 --> 01:48:53,556
Annachi's henchmen are destroying shops
in the market. - You sit down.

1575
01:48:53,927 --> 01:48:55,792
They've killed the shopkeepers.

1576
01:48:55,996 --> 01:48:58,726
Not only that, they've hacked
4 policemen too.

1577
01:48:58,932 --> 01:49:01,560
They're hitting women & children too.

1578
01:49:01,768 --> 01:49:03,133
Come & see there. - Come.

1579
01:49:07,941 --> 01:49:09,408
Sir... sir... Did you see this?

1580
01:49:09,609 --> 01:49:11,668
We've lost all our goods.

1581
01:49:11,878 --> 01:49:14,438
Look, they've killed our men.

1582
01:49:20,453 --> 01:49:23,251
Sir, we opened our shops because you
told us to open them.

1583
01:49:23,623 --> 01:49:25,921
Look, what Annachi's men have
done to us?

1584
01:49:26,726 --> 01:49:29,422
Look there, they've destroyed
all the shops.

1585
01:49:32,065 --> 01:49:35,592
He was in the market.
They killed him & went away.

1586
01:49:35,802 --> 01:49:38,100
l don't know what to do.
l'm clueless.

1587
01:49:38,305 --> 01:49:43,607
Did you see? Look how brutal they are.

1588
01:49:45,478 --> 01:49:48,447
We opened our shops because
you told us to open them.

1589
01:49:48,815 --> 01:49:51,113
Scoundrels, they've killed our men.

1590
01:49:51,651 --> 01:49:56,281
Look at this brutality!
What crime have we committed?

1591
01:49:57,157 --> 01:49:59,284
Why should we suffer like this?

1592
01:49:59,492 --> 01:50:02,290
Stop madam.. stop..

1593
01:50:03,663 --> 01:50:04,721
Look at this brutality.

1594
01:50:05,332 --> 01:50:06,799
They all opened the shops because we
told them to open.

1595
01:50:07,000 --> 01:50:08,297
What should we do with Annachi?

1596
01:50:08,501 --> 01:50:09,798
What're we going to do for them?

1597
01:50:25,185 --> 01:50:25,810
Stop sir.

1598
01:50:29,122 --> 01:50:30,487
Come Saamy.

1599
01:50:30,857 --> 01:50:33,826
Have you come to get my blessings
after marriage.

1600
01:50:34,527 --> 01:50:35,824
Where's your wife?

1601
01:50:36,363 --> 01:50:36,988
Hey stop!

1602
01:50:37,197 --> 01:50:39,995
Hey, do you know the value of life?

1603
01:50:40,867 --> 01:50:43,768
Since your name is Saamy(God), did you
think you're God of this City?

1604
01:50:45,271 --> 01:50:47,831
Who permitted you to give them
Police protection?

1605
01:50:48,041 --> 01:50:49,838
Whom do l have to ask?
- You must ask me.

1606
01:50:50,043 --> 01:50:51,305
Are you the Collector or
the Government?

1607
01:50:51,511 --> 01:50:52,671
l'm more than that.

1608
01:50:53,713 --> 01:50:59,515
With Rs.13,000 salary, 2 sets
of uniforms & a pair of shoes,

1609
01:50:59,886 --> 01:51:02,855
Controlling 4 police stations
& 40 police men,

1610
01:51:03,056 --> 01:51:05,854
You've so much of arrogance?

1611
01:51:06,393 --> 01:51:10,193
l control 8 districts,
92 MLA's & 16 MP's,

1612
01:51:10,397 --> 01:51:15,198
And l control the Government.
How arrogant l should be?

1613
01:51:15,402 --> 01:51:18,701
Hey, l read 20 Newspapers a day.

1614
01:51:19,072 --> 01:51:21,540
Do you think it's easy to
indulge in Politics?

1615
01:51:21,741 --> 01:51:26,041
My high command is continuously
seeking information about the strike.

1616
01:51:26,246 --> 01:51:27,713
Will you answer them?

1617
01:51:29,582 --> 01:51:32,710
l don't have any value
for lives.

1618
01:51:32,919 --> 01:51:37,720
You made me lose my honour.
So, l took revenge.

1619
01:51:39,259 --> 01:51:40,055
lf you wanted to take revenge,

1620
01:51:40,260 --> 01:51:41,955
You must've fought with me for
giving them protection.

1621
01:51:42,929 --> 01:51:45,056
But you've killed innocent
businessmen.

1622
01:51:45,265 --> 01:51:47,733
You've broken the heads of women
& children too.

1623
01:51:47,934 --> 01:51:49,902
2 Policemen have died.
Who'll answer their families?

1624
01:51:50,670 --> 01:51:53,002
You people get salaries to die.

1625
01:51:53,206 --> 01:51:56,232
You're proud that you're part of
the fighting force, aren't you?

1626
01:51:56,609 --> 01:51:57,906
You must die when it
comes to fight.

1627
01:51:58,111 --> 01:52:01,239
Hey, we'll compensate for the
lost lives & damaged shops.

1628
01:52:01,448 --> 01:52:03,746
You Police dogs will wag your tail
if we give you bribes,

1629
01:52:03,950 --> 01:52:05,076
Or else you'll bark at us.

1630
01:52:05,285 --> 01:52:08,743
l don't bark, l bite!

1631
01:52:09,622 --> 01:52:12,750
l would've cut your throat on the day you
entered my house without permission.

1632
01:52:13,626 --> 01:52:16,925
