02:06:02,988 --> 02:06:05,582
Move! l want to see the groom & bride.
Move...move...

1866
02:06:07,626 --> 02:06:10,925
What's this? The bride looks
like a donkey.

1867
02:06:11,297 --> 02:06:13,857
Donkey is the bride.
- ls donkey the bride?

1868
02:06:14,967 --> 02:06:15,763
What's this?

1869
02:06:16,302 --> 02:06:18,429
You can have marriage
between different castes.

1870
02:06:18,637 --> 02:06:20,264
lnter-religion marriages
are also acceptable.

1871
02:06:20,472 --> 02:06:24,431
But you've become too modern
by marrying a donkey.

1872
02:06:24,643 --> 02:06:25,610
There is no rain for
the past 2 years.

1873
02:06:25,811 --> 02:06:28,439
According to a tradition, if anyone
marries a donkey, a chameleon or a frog.

1874
02:06:28,647 --> 02:06:29,443
lt'll rain, won't it?

1875
02:06:30,149 --> 02:06:33,778
Why don't you marry a lion?
- lt'll eat me alive.

1876
02:06:33,986 --> 02:06:34,953
You know that, don't you?

1877
02:06:35,154 --> 02:06:37,622
Why're you still superstitious?

1878
02:06:38,157 --> 02:06:39,624
You're breaking a coconut
on tonsured head.

1879
02:06:39,825 --> 02:06:42,293
lf it bleeds, you'll call it
as wrath of God.

1880
02:06:42,494 --> 02:06:46,294
You're offering goat, hen, pig, buffalo
& everything other than man.

1881
02:06:46,498 --> 02:06:48,466
Then you eat everything.
What's all this?

1882
02:06:48,667 --> 02:06:51,227
You had taken the advance
to conduct the marriage.

1883
02:06:52,338 --> 02:06:53,635
Never let go an opportunity
to threaten people.

1884
02:06:54,506 --> 02:06:56,474
Take this auspicious thread and
tie the knot. - Recite the hymns.

1885
02:06:57,009 --> 02:06:57,634
Hymn?

1886
02:07:03,515 --> 02:07:04,709
Stop it. This isn't a hymn.

1887
02:07:05,517 --> 02:07:08,486
This hymn is enough for
donkey's marriage.

1888
02:07:08,687 --> 02:07:09,654
Tie the auspicious thread.

1889
02:07:09,855 --> 02:07:13,985
My grandson is coming
majestically like a lion.

1890
02:07:14,193 --> 02:07:17,253
Anyone crossing swords with him
will not be able to bear his kick.

1891
02:07:22,534 --> 02:07:25,162
Hey, donkey got enraged and kicked
his sensitive part.

1892
02:07:26,872 --> 02:07:29,670
This donkey has become
punching donkey.

1893
02:07:29,875 --> 02:07:32,673
You all planned a marriage
of the donkey.

1894
02:07:32,878 --> 02:07:36,279
But, this donkey has made
him impotent.

1895
02:07:36,882 --> 02:07:37,678
What's this sir?

1896
02:07:37,916 --> 02:07:40,043
They're planning a protest for reservation
and presenting a memorandum.

1897
02:07:40,219 --> 02:07:41,345
You've permitted them.

1898
02:07:41,553 --> 02:07:42,679
Two MLA's are leading
the procession.

1899
02:07:42,888 --> 02:07:44,185
Minister ordered me to permit them.

1900
02:07:44,390 --> 02:07:45,516
What can l do other
than permit them?

1901
02:07:45,724 --> 02:07:47,521
You restrict yourself to
security arrangements only.

1902
02:07:48,394 --> 02:07:50,521
Sir, what happened?
- He has given them the permission.

1903
02:07:50,729 --> 02:07:52,697
Then, you don't stay here.
- What are you saying?

1904
02:07:52,898 --> 02:07:54,866
They all are very angry with you.

1905
02:07:55,401 --> 02:07:57,369
2 years ago just like this,
They planned a procession.

1906
02:07:57,569 --> 02:07:59,366
And ransacked Melapalayam
Police station.

1907
02:07:59,571 --> 02:08:01,300
Four people hacked
the lnspector to death.

1908
02:08:01,740 --> 02:08:05,039
As the procession crosses Corporation
office starting from bus station.

1909
02:08:05,577 --> 02:08:06,703
There's a petty shop
which belongs to our man.

1910
02:08:06,912 --> 02:08:08,777
Soda water bottles will be
supplied from there.

1911
02:08:09,081 --> 02:08:10,378
That's their first weapon.

1912
02:08:10,582 --> 02:08:12,049
Further up from there,
it's ''Kandappa lathe works.''

1913
02:08:12,251 --> 02:08:13,548
We'll get sickles from there.

1914
02:08:13,752 --> 02:08:15,879
They'll try to attack us as soon as
they get hold of the weapons.

1915
02:08:16,088 --> 02:08:19,057
Since the Collector is out of station,
they'll not get firing orders.

1916
02:08:19,258 --> 02:08:22,227
They'll cross their limits thinking
that we'll not get firing orders.

1917
02:08:22,428 --> 02:08:23,224
l'll take care of that.

1918
02:08:23,429 --> 02:08:25,397
As procession nears the police station,
...clashes must break out.

1919
02:08:25,497 --> 02:08:28,295
ln that, police station and
Saamy, both must be annihilated.

1920
02:08:28,600 --> 02:08:31,330
Files which we can't be closed legally
must be closed illegally.

1921
02:08:31,603 --> 02:08:33,730
Sir, you're saying that....
- You'll understand.

1922
02:08:34,606 --> 02:08:35,903
Another very important thing.

1923
02:08:36,775 --> 02:08:39,573
No pressmen must photograph the event.
Even if they manage,

1924
02:08:39,778 --> 02:08:41,336
Only smoke must be seen in
those photos, okay?

1925
02:08:43,282 --> 02:08:45,409
We'll be in trouble only if they
cross corporation office.

1926
02:08:46,618 --> 02:08:47,414
They'll never cross it.

1927
02:08:47,619 --> 02:08:53,751
ls this strength enough
or do you want more?

1928
02:08:53,959 --> 02:08:56,757
How dare you challenge our Boss?

1929
02:08:56,962 --> 02:09:00,420
We'll fight till we get justice.

1930
02:09:00,632 --> 02:09:06,935
Remove... - Poverty...

1931
02:09:07,139 --> 02:09:10,267
Don't take away...
- Don't take away our rights.

1932
02:09:10,476 --> 02:09:17,780
Handcuff the police.
We'll give them a run for their money.

1933
02:09:17,983 --> 02:09:20,383
Today, they're in for some boons from Saamy(God).

1934
02:09:22,654 --> 02:09:24,281
They're raising slogans without
knowing our D.C.

1935
02:09:25,991 --> 02:09:28,789
Sir, as soon as we cross Corporation
office, we'll get weapons.

1936
02:09:29,161 --> 02:09:31,721
l'll make the first kill of D.C.
- Okay.

1937
02:09:31,930 --> 02:09:33,124
We must do as sir has ordered us.

1938
02:09:33,332 --> 02:09:35,800
Hello... - We'll be reaching
Corporation office shortly.

1939
02:09:36,001 --> 02:09:37,730
We are ready.
- You must strictly follow my orders.

1940
02:09:43,509 --> 02:09:45,306
We are hearing. - Okay sir.

1941
02:09:46,678 --> 02:09:48,407
Get the ambulance ready.
- Okay, sir.

1942
02:09:50,015 --> 02:09:53,815
We are going to teach a
lesson to the police.

1943
02:09:54,019 --> 02:10:00,322
Don't take away our rights.

1944
02:10:00,526 --> 02:10:04,826
Tirunelveli district is going
to teach you a lesson.

1945
02:10:05,030 --> 02:10:05,655
Baton charge.

1946
02:10:08,700 --> 02:10:09,667
Ambulance is ready.

1947
02:10:21,880 --> 02:10:23,347
Hey, who's throwing
stones at us?

1948
02:10:23,549 --> 02:10:24,345
Stop it.

1949
02:10:24,716 --> 02:10:25,182
Beat them back, boys.

1950
02:10:26,051 --> 02:10:27,916
Baton charge!

1951
02:10:29,054 --> 02:10:31,181
Down with Police atrocities....

1952
02:10:31,390 --> 02:10:32,857
Hey, stop.

1953
02:10:33,725 --> 02:10:39,357
Down with the Police atrocities.

1954
02:10:42,067 --> 02:10:43,364
Tear gas.

1955
02:10:47,906 --> 02:10:49,703
Hey, don't spare them.
Beat them.

1956
02:11:24,776 --> 02:11:25,242
Go away.

1957
02:11:35,787 --> 02:11:37,914
You raped my sister.

1958
02:11:39,625 --> 02:11:41,525
Hereafter you can never rape any girl.

1959
02:11:46,798 --> 02:11:49,266
Hey, how dare you catch me?
l'm an MLA.

1960
02:11:49,468 --> 02:11:49,991
Come, man.

1961
02:11:52,304 --> 02:11:53,999
How can l fire without orders?

1962
02:11:54,473 --> 02:11:56,600
My pistol and six bullets are here.

1963
02:11:56,808 --> 02:11:57,274
Then, who shot them dead?

1964
02:11:57,476 --> 02:11:59,774
5000 people were in that procession.
10,000 people were watching the fun.

1965
02:11:59,978 --> 02:12:01,104
How can l know who shot them dead?

1966
02:12:01,313 --> 02:12:02,940
So, l was against giving
them permission.

1967
02:12:03,148 --> 02:12:04,615
Now, you're responsible for
all the trouble.

1968
02:12:04,983 --> 02:12:07,451
Okay! Atleast release that
Athankarai Shanmugam.

1969
02:12:07,653 --> 02:12:09,280
Till l get clear evidence
about the death of 3 people,

1970
02:12:09,488 --> 02:12:10,284
l'll not release them.

1971
02:12:10,489 --> 02:12:13,117
Are you talking so bravely as your
records are straight?

1972
02:12:13,659 --> 02:12:15,627
You don't know the
reach of Annachi!

1973
02:12:15,827 --> 02:12:17,124
l don't want to know.

1974
02:12:27,005 --> 02:12:27,630
Greetings sir.

1975
02:12:27,839 --> 02:12:30,307
Why're you greeting me, man?
Fire...fire at me.

1976
02:12:31,009 --> 02:12:33,569
He shot my men.
You fire at me.

1977
02:12:33,845 --> 02:12:35,244
Welcome, Perumal Pitchai.

1978
02:12:35,681 --> 02:12:40,311
You've killed my men and accounted
their deaths under communal clashes.

1979
02:12:40,519 --> 02:12:43,317
lt's true, l shot them dead, then.
lt's true your men saw me.

1980
02:12:43,522 --> 02:12:44,318
But, there are no records.

1981
02:12:44,523 --> 02:12:48,983
Hey, are you teaching me the game
in which l'm an expert?

1982
02:12:49,194 --> 02:12:50,991
lf there's a reason,
l'll use Government pistol.

1983
02:12:51,196 --> 02:12:52,493
Or else an illegal pistol.

1984
02:12:52,864 --> 02:12:54,661
A sickle used by anyone
will hurt you.

1985
02:12:55,200 --> 02:12:56,997
A pistol fired by
anyone will kill.

1986
02:12:57,869 --> 02:12:58,665
Watch out, in 2 days...

1987
02:12:58,870 --> 02:12:59,837
How dare you point your
finger at Annachi?

1988
02:13:00,038 --> 02:13:01,665
Oh, shouldn't l talk pointing
a finger at him?

1989
02:13:06,545 --> 02:13:10,504
l'll make you run away
leaving everything behind.

1990
02:13:10,716 --> 02:13:15,176
Down with police atrocities.

1991
02:13:15,387 --> 02:13:21,690
People waiting outside will kill any
number of people on a hint from me.

1992
02:13:21,893 --> 02:13:25,021
The guns here will fire at any
number of people on my orders.

1993
02:13:25,230 --> 02:13:27,198
l'll immolate here for Annachi.

1994
02:13:28,734 --> 02:13:30,702
l'll immolate here.

1995
02:13:30,902 --> 02:13:38,206
Down with Police atrocities.

1996
02:13:38,410 --> 02:13:39,877
l'll immolate for Annachi.

1997
02:13:45,250 --> 02:13:46,649
l think he'll really burn us down...
Run away from here.

1998
02:13:47,753 --> 02:13:48,378
Run away.

1999
02:13:53,425 --> 02:13:54,722
l'm like a live wire.

2000
02:13:55,260 --> 02:13:56,659
lf you touch, you can't
bear the shock.

2001
02:14:01,933 --> 02:14:04,401
He has insulted us.
Annachi, what shall we do now?

2002
02:14:04,603 --> 02:14:08,130
lnform our boys in Kaitharu
and get him lynched.

2003
02:14:08,774 --> 02:14:11,072
l was never afraid even when l
went against the British.

2004
02:14:11,443 --> 02:14:14,469
But, l'm damn scared
of these murderers.

2005
02:14:15,447 --> 02:14:18,416
l'm anticipating trouble here
any moment.

2006
02:14:18,617 --> 02:14:20,244
When there are so many
policemen around,

2007
02:14:20,452 --> 02:14:22,579
And when they are not bothered,
why are you?

2008
02:14:22,788 --> 02:14:25,916
Son-in-law, everyone has come
out with fear.

2009
02:14:26,124 --> 02:14:27,591
l don't know what to say.

2010
02:14:27,959 --> 02:14:32,589
You both must be safe & happy.

2011
02:14:32,964 --> 02:14:35,592
Anyway, you're going out from
here on a transfer.

2012
02:14:35,801 --> 02:14:38,429
You go away today.
No one will be in any trouble.

2013
02:14:38,637 --> 02:14:41,538
Son-in-law...
- Father, all of you may go now.

2014
02:14:42,407 --> 02:14:43,339
Nothing will happen to me.

2015
02:14:44,242 --> 02:14:45,869
You don't unnecessarily
make him tense.

2016
02:14:46,645 --> 02:14:47,111
Please go away.

2017
02:14:50,816 --> 02:14:55,378
Did you send them out to pacify me?
Or are you really confident about me?

2018
02:14:56,321 --> 02:14:58,846
lf anything happens to me,
you'll be the worst affected.

2019
02:14:59,991 --> 02:15:01,959
lf your confidence in me has dipped
even by 1 percent, tell me.

2020
02:15:02,427 --> 02:15:03,223
We'll leave this place.

2021
02:15:05,664 --> 02:15:09,964
l've 100% confidence in you.
You'll definitely win.

2022
02:15:14,906 --> 02:15:17,704
Brother, son-in-law hasn't taken
any of our advise.

2023
02:15:18,009 --> 02:15:22,036
You advise him. - You don't worry.
l'll talk to him.

2024
02:15:29,688 --> 02:15:32,156
Are you scared? - No.

2025
02:15:32,357 --> 02:15:33,585
Why're your eyes
filled with tears?

2026
02:15:34,192 --> 02:15:35,056
Sacred ash fell into my eyes.

2027
02:15:35,360 --> 02:15:36,987
Son, where are you?
- ln the temple, father.

2028
02:15:37,195 --> 02:15:38,492
l heard you had been transferred.

2029
02:15:38,697 --> 02:15:39,994
l heard you're in some trouble.

2030
02:15:40,198 --> 02:15:41,165
Shall l come there?

2031
02:15:41,366 --> 02:15:42,663
No need. Problem will be
solved in 2 days.

2032
02:15:43,034 --> 02:15:44,001
l'll come back there.

2033
02:15:44,202 --> 02:15:45,169
Don't unnecessarily come here.

2034
02:15:45,537 --> 02:15:46,003
Okay, son.

2035
02:16:03,221 --> 02:16:04,916
Bhuvana, remove your slippers and
go into the temple immediately.

2036
02:16:05,123 --> 02:16:05,589
Why?

2037
02:16:05,957 --> 02:16:06,685
Just follow my orders.

2038
02:16:07,292 --> 02:16:08,088
Sister, take her.

2039
02:17:06,751 --> 02:17:11,211
Can't you understand why a man
is running away with a pistol?

2040
02:17:13,024 --> 02:17:16,289
lf l beat you in front of the temple,
it'll be a disturbance to devotees.

2041
02:17:18,029 --> 02:17:22,591
lt's better to slaughter a goat in
a closed area than on the road.

2042
02:17:27,806 --> 02:17:28,534
What're you looking at?

2043
02:17:29,674 --> 02:17:31,665
God will get into a trance only
when drums are beaten.

2044
02:19:08,206 --> 02:19:10,766
Saamy has told you not to go there.
Why're you going there?

2045
02:19:10,975 --> 02:19:15,071
No, l'm anxious.
l'll check personally.

2046
02:19:15,280 --> 02:19:17,214
Bhuvana, you leave for
Palani immediately. - Why?

2047
02:19:17,415 --> 02:19:18,780
We've just 24 hours.

2048
02:19:19,284 --> 02:19:20,774
You mustn't get into any
trouble before that.

2049
02:19:21,486 --> 02:19:22,714
l'll come there by
tomorrow evening.

2050
02:19:22,987 --> 02:19:24,113
Who's going with you?

2051
02:19:24,322 --> 02:19:25,220
l'm going alone, mother.

2052
02:19:25,423 --> 02:19:26,617
Go safely, dear.

2053
02:19:26,825 --> 02:19:27,291
Okay, mother.

2054
02:19:28,760 --> 02:19:29,226
Tell me, Babu.

2055
02:19:29,427 --> 02:19:32,396
Perumal Pitchai talked to
Pattasu Raman of Sivakasi.

2056
02:19:32,597 --> 02:19:33,256
What did he say?

2057
02:19:33,465 --> 02:19:36,400
He said we must create a
`loud noise' in Tirunelveli.

2058
02:19:36,901 --> 02:19:39,665
l think `loud noise' is
their code word.

2059
02:19:40,739 --> 02:19:42,468
ln Sivakasi, bursting of crackers
will make loud noise.

2060
02:19:42,674 --> 02:19:45,142
Crackers, loud noise?
Anything connected with bomb?

2061
02:19:46,511 --> 02:19:47,307
lt must be a bomb.

2062
02:19:47,579 --> 02:19:51,208
l want to talk to you...Come...

2063
02:19:52,183 --> 02:19:53,741
No. l'll get into the jeep
without warrant.

2064
02:19:54,986 --> 02:19:55,884
l've not come in a jeep.

2065
02:19:56,221 --> 02:19:59,748
You're facing charges of 4 murders, arson,
stabbing and many other crimes.

2066
02:20:00,024 --> 02:20:02,584
We can put you in jail
for 12 years.

2067
02:20:03,862 --> 02:20:07,491
Or else with one shot,
l can close the file as a murder.

2068
02:20:09,701 --> 02:20:10,429
Don't get scared.

2069
02:20:11,369 --> 02:20:12,996
l would've killed you that day,
if had l wanted to.

2070
02:20:14,205 --> 02:20:16,002
When l shot others,
l saw only individuals.

2071
02:20:16,207 --> 02:20:19,005
But, when l aimed at you,
l saw your wife & children.

2072
02:20:19,711 --> 02:20:20,507
lf you follow my orders.

2073
02:20:20,712 --> 02:20:23,408
l'll dilute the cases so that you'll
get 2 or 3 years jail term.

2074
02:20:23,748 --> 02:20:24,237
What do you say?

2075
02:20:25,483 --> 02:20:26,848
l'll always keep up my promise.

2076
02:20:27,886 --> 02:20:28,511
Okay.

2077
02:20:28,720 --> 02:20:33,248
Annachi has called Pattasu Raman
to plant a bomb here. - Why?

2078
02:20:34,058 --> 02:20:35,525
To plant a bomb in your house.

2079
02:20:35,727 --> 02:20:37,024
What're you saying man?

2080
02:20:37,228 --> 02:20:41,358
He has asked him plant the bomb
to go off at 10.30 p.m.

2081
02:20:41,966 --> 02:20:43,763
And asked him to stay
at Hotel Sugam.

2082
02:20:43,968 --> 02:20:45,196
Sir, let's go immediately. - No.

2083
02:20:47,238 --> 02:20:48,034
Let the bomb go off.

2084
02:20:49,073 --> 02:20:50,040
What're you saying sir?

2085
02:20:51,743 --> 02:20:53,711
This is the only way to
arrest Perumal Pitchai.

2086
02:20:53,912 --> 02:20:55,880
He has become an approver.
We can arrest Pattasu Raman.

2087
02:20:56,080 --> 02:20:58,207
With this evidence we can arrest him.
- Case will not stand in the court.

2088
02:20:58,783 --> 02:21:00,717
Because of the influence he has,
he'll walk out freely.

2089
02:21:01,252 --> 02:21:01,980
Let my house get blasted off.

2090
02:21:02,420 --> 02:21:04,684
Only then, l can arrest him under
Terrorist act. - Then, Bhuvana?

2091
02:21:04,889 --> 02:21:05,787
She's on the way to Palani.

2092
02:21:05,990 --> 02:21:08,049
Look, the bomb will
blast at 10.30 p.m.

2093
02:21:08,259 --> 02:21:10,056
Arrest Pattasu Raman
exactly at 10.35 p.m.

2094
02:21:10,261 --> 02:21:11,728
l'll go & meet the Commissioner. - Why?

2095
02:21:13,198 --> 02:21:14,995
Department must know Annachi
has planted a bomb.

2096
02:21:15,733 --> 02:21:17,098
But they mustn't
know the location.

2097
02:21:17,435 --> 02:21:19,027
No one can harm my son.

2098
02:21:19,671 --> 02:21:21,400
lf you all stay here,
he'll give up a winning race.

2099
02:21:22,207 --> 02:21:24,072
And spend his entire energy
to save your lives.

2100
02:21:24,275 --> 02:21:25,867
So, go to Palani immediately.

2101
02:21:26,211 --> 02:21:28,372
No one can harm my son
till l'm alive.

2102
02:21:28,613 --> 02:21:30,012
l'll come with him tomorrow.

2103
02:21:30,215 --> 02:21:33,082
Pattasu Raman come immediately. We must
create a loud noise in Tirunelveli.

2104
02:21:35,153 --> 02:21:39,419
lf we touch Annachi, we'll get orders
from C.M.. Who'll face the consequences.

2105
02:21:39,624 --> 02:21:42,092
lf we don't take any action
and the bomb goes off.

2106
02:21:42,293 --> 02:21:44,261
Still, we've to face the heat from C.M.
- Everything is your doing.

2107
02:21:44,462 --> 02:21:46,760
For the action you took against them
in the procession.

2108
02:21:46,965 --> 02:21:49,593
Tell me your decision to
solve this problem.

2109
02:21:50,802 --> 02:21:52,929
First, send a message of alert
to all police stations.

2110
02:22:00,144 --> 02:22:01,111
Sir, here are the keys.

2111
02:22:02,847 --> 02:22:03,871
Shall l get you something to eat?

2112
02:22:04,082 --> 02:22:07,381
No need. l'll eat along
with my son. - Okay sir.

2113
02:22:21,866 --> 02:22:22,457
Hello.

2114
02:22:22,667 --> 02:22:23,861
l'm Saamy's father speaking.

2115
02:22:24,068 --> 02:22:25,558
Sir has gone to meet Commissioner.

2116
02:22:25,837 --> 02:22:26,633
You call him on his cell phone.

2117
02:22:29,374 --> 02:22:31,171
Sir is in a meeting
with Commissioner.

2118
02:22:31,342 --> 02:22:32,809
So, he has left his phone with me.

2119
02:22:33,077 --> 02:22:35,568
Tell him, l've come here.
l'll talk to him later.

2120
02:22:39,450 --> 02:22:40,747
Sir, you got a call
from your father.

2121
02:22:43,354 --> 02:22:45,322
From where did he call me?
- He called from your house only.

2122
02:22:46,658 --> 02:22:47,215
What are you saying?

2123
02:22:47,525 --> 02:22:49,152
He said he had come just now
from your native place.

2124
02:22:49,527 --> 02:22:51,154
Oh shit!

2125
02:22:58,870 --> 02:23:01,498
My daughter-in-law and her
relatives are coming there.

2126
02:23:01,706 --> 02:23:03,833
Take good care of them.
- Okay sir.

2127
02:23:06,878 --> 02:23:08,175
They're strict vegetarians.

2128
02:23:08,379 --> 02:23:10,176
Tell servants to clean the
vessels thoroughly.

2129
02:23:11,549 --> 02:23:14,347
lt seems some Perumal Pitchai
is troubling my son.

2130
02:23:14,886 --> 02:23:17,013
l'll kill him myself
and go to jail.

2131
02:23:17,221 --> 02:23:18,882
But, l'll not allow him
to touch my son.

2132
02:23:26,564 --> 02:23:27,963
Father, come out of the
house immediately.

2133
02:23:28,166 --> 02:23:28,757
Why?

2134
02:23:28,967 --> 02:23:30,798
A bomb has been planted in our house.
Come out immediately.

2135
02:23:31,736 --> 02:23:32,202
What?

2136
02:23:35,740 --> 02:23:36,365
Oh my god!

2137
02:23:43,915 --> 02:23:44,540
Father...

2138
02:23:46,017 --> 02:23:48,645
Father...

2139
02:23:49,253 --> 02:23:50,379
Father...

2140
02:23:59,430 --> 02:24:00,055
Father...

2141
02:24:01,265 --> 02:24:01,890
Father...

2142
02:24:18,082 --> 02:24:20,550
Father...

2143
02:24:34,799 --> 02:24:36,426
He has been with
Annachi for 16 years.

2144
02:24:36,968 --> 02:24:38,265
l wish to become an approver.

2145
02:24:44,142 --> 02:24:45,700
l heard about it...sorry.

2146
02:24:48,646 --> 02:24:49,203
Best of luck.

2147
02:24:49,480 --> 02:24:51,607
l told you to keep cool for 2 days.

2148
02:24:51,983 --> 02:24:53,280
Why did you plant
a bomb in his house?

2149
02:24:53,484 --> 02:24:55,213
Already he's after you
like a mad dog.

2150
02:24:55,653 --> 02:24:57,848
He made a fool proof
case against you.

2151
02:24:58,056 --> 02:24:59,455
And has taken arrest
warrant against you.

2152
02:24:59,657 --> 02:25:04,959
l can't help you anymore. Abscond for a
day or get yourself arrested.

2153
02:25:05,496 --> 02:25:07,123
Whom are you suggesting
to surrender?

2154
02:25:07,432 --> 02:25:10,128
lf l get arrested, Tirunelveli will
rise against him.

2155
02:25:10,668 --> 02:25:12,295
lnsult...it's an insult.

2156
02:25:12,670 --> 02:25:15,969
Getting arrested is impossible
in my life.

2157
02:25:16,174 --> 02:25:18,802
Okay. l'll talk to him
once again for you.

2158
02:25:20,678 --> 02:25:25,138
Hey, kill everyone in his family.

2159
02:25:25,349 --> 02:25:27,647
He has already packed them
all to his native place.

2160
02:25:33,958 --> 02:25:36,256
Sir, call from the Commissioner.

2161
02:25:36,461 --> 02:25:39,589
An urgent secret meeting has
been arranged in our Dept.

2162
02:25:39,797 --> 02:25:40,923
You must come immediately.

2163
02:25:41,466 --> 02:25:44,435
Ministers, MLAs, District Collectors
from 8 districts are coming.

2164
02:25:44,635 --> 02:25:45,602
You must attend without fail.

2165
02:25:47,805 --> 02:25:48,328
Hello...

2166
02:25:48,639 --> 02:25:49,765
l'm DC's wife speaking.

2167
02:25:50,141 --> 02:25:51,199
House phone is not responding,

2168
02:25:51,409 --> 02:25:52,273
l'm not able to reach him
on cell phone also.

2169
02:25:52,577 --> 02:25:54,602
Please give him the phone.
- Sir is in hospital.

2170
02:25:54,812 --> 02:25:55,938
Why? What happened to him?

2171
02:25:56,147 --> 02:25:57,614
Don't you know house was
blasted off with a bomb?

2172
02:25:57,815 --> 02:25:58,281
What're you saying?

2173
02:25:58,483 --> 02:26:02,442
Don't tell her. - Hello...hello...
What happened to him?

2174
02:26:02,653 --> 02:26:04,120
Sir is safe.
You don't worry.

2175
02:26:04,655 --> 02:26:05,451
Why did you tell her?

2176
02:26:05,656 --> 02:26:07,180
lt's midnight now.
You want to go there.

2177
02:26:07,391 --> 02:26:08,790
Your parents are on the way.

2178
02:26:08,993 --> 02:26:12,690
Even if l catch the last bus.
l'll reach by morning.

2179
02:26:12,897 --> 02:26:14,296
Drop me at bus stand.

2180
02:26:16,400 --> 02:26:18,061
Mr.Saamy, please don't
arrest Annachi.

2181
02:26:18,269 --> 02:26:20,464
lf you arrest him, it'll
create political problems.

2182
02:26:20,671 --> 02:26:23,139
Sorry sir. l don't care about it.

2183
02:26:23,341 --> 02:26:24,808
His influence extends from
State to Central level.

2184
02:26:25,343 --> 02:26:27,311
You're not going to
stay here tomorrow.

2185
02:26:27,512 --> 02:26:28,638
Then, why're you creating
trouble for him?

2186
02:26:28,846 --> 02:26:31,872
Ten years ago, you were
a vegetable seller.

2187
02:26:32,083 --> 02:26:32,981
Today, you're a Minister.

2188
02:26:33,351 --> 02:26:34,648
You own 5 colleges.

2189
02:26:34,852 --> 02:26:35,648
You don't say a word.

2190
02:26:36,187 --> 02:26:37,484
Why're you talking bad about him?

2191
02:26:37,688 --> 02:26:41,647
You're telling me not to arrest
an accused? - Are you Mr.Clean?

2192
02:26:42,026 --> 02:26:45,826
You had taken Rs.34 lakhs as
bribe from Annachi. - Deny it.

2193
02:26:46,864 --> 02:26:48,195
No.

2194
02:26:49,934 --> 02:26:53,836
He has given the list of bribes
he gave you, date-wise.

2195
02:26:55,873 --> 02:26:59,832
l didn't take Rs.34 lakhs,
but Rs.36 lakhs 50 thousand.

2196
02:27:00,745 --> 02:27:02,906
l was about to tell that he had
left out a few payments.

2197
02:27:04,715 --> 02:27:05,773
l've full account of it.

2198
02:27:06,551 --> 02:27:07,518
The money he paid me on a date....

2199
02:27:07,718 --> 02:27:08,946
l've sent it to Gujarat
Earth quake relief fund.

2200
02:27:09,153 --> 02:27:10,381
Orissa starvation deaths,
cyclone relief fund...

2201
02:27:10,588 --> 02:27:12,749
To CM's welfare fund...

2202
02:27:12,957 --> 02:27:14,720
l've receipts on his name
as money sent by him.

2203
02:27:22,800 --> 02:27:23,698
What're you looking at?

2204
02:27:24,101 --> 02:27:26,365
Annachi is not a meek cat to kick.

2205
02:27:26,571 --> 02:27:27,037
He's an Elephant.

2206
02:27:27,805 --> 02:27:28,737
We must get on its head to beat it.

2207
02:27:29,407 --> 02:27:31,534
So, l took money from him
and his built trust on me.

2208
02:27:32,410 --> 02:27:33,035
Now, l'm beating him.

2209
02:27:33,411 --> 02:27:34,639
Then, you took Rs.4 lakhs
from a killer.

2210
02:27:34,912 --> 02:27:36,880
And Rs.3 lakhs from a man
who ran over another man...

2211
02:27:37,248 --> 02:27:38,215
On what account?

2212
02:27:40,418 --> 02:27:41,214
Justice Account!

2213
02:27:42,587 --> 02:27:43,713
lf we arrest any who runs over
another man with his car.

2214
02:27:43,921 --> 02:27:44,888
You'll jail him for 3 months.

2215
02:27:45,089 --> 02:27:46,113
He'll pay Rs.3000 as fine
and goes out scott free.

2216
02:27:46,324 --> 02:27:47,552
Who'll feed the victim's family?

2217
02:27:48,960 --> 02:27:50,894
So, l took Rs.4 lakhs from him and
paid it to the victim's family.

2218
02:27:52,096 --> 02:27:53,893
l'm concerned about dead man
than the killer.

2219
02:27:54,765 --> 02:27:56,562
Tell me, if anyone has complained that
l've taken bribe from general public.

2220
02:27:56,767 --> 02:27:58,291
l'll kill myself at that very moment.

2221
02:27:59,770 --> 02:28:03,228
A man living on bribes will not have
2 sets of uniform & torn socks.

2222
02:28:04,609 --> 02:28:09,069
To join police! My father is still paying
interest on Rs.2 lakhs loan.

2223
02:28:09,447 --> 02:28:10,311
Leave it.

2224
02:28:10,681 --> 02:28:14,082
Are you running a police station
according to law or a jungle justice?

2225
02:28:14,452 --> 02:28:17,910
Will you change laws like
you change clothes?

2226
02:28:18,122 --> 02:28:19,248
What's so great about law?

2227
02:28:20,291 --> 02:28:21,758
When Tamil Nadu was
under Prohibition,

2228
02:28:21,959 --> 02:28:23,256
lf anyone drinks in Pondicherry
it's not a crime.

2229
02:28:23,794 --> 02:28:25,694
But, if he comes to nearby
Cuddalore, it's a crime.

2230
02:28:26,797 --> 02:28:29,265
Prostitution is legal in
Mumbai according to law.

2231
02:28:30,468 --> 02:28:31,594
The same thing is illegal here.

2232
02:28:32,970 --> 02:28:34,597
A law for each caste & state.

2233
02:28:35,473 --> 02:28:35,996
Forget about all that.

2234
02:28:37,308 --> 02:28:39,435
l've not yet performed
my dead father's last rites.

2235
02:28:40,144 --> 02:28:43,341
You're asking me not to arrest
his killer. What's this law?

2236
02:28:43,547 --> 02:28:45,606
What's your final decision?
- l'm saying that l'll arrest him.

2237
02:28:45,917 --> 02:28:48,283
l may be forced to stop you
from arresting him,

2238
02:28:48,653 --> 02:28:49,278
Are you threatening me?

2239
02:28:50,154 --> 02:28:51,951
l came into this world
killing five people.

2240
02:28:52,890 --> 02:28:54,619
lf anyone stops me in
discharging my duty.

2241
02:28:55,493 --> 02:28:56,721
l'll kill anyone
& any number of people.

2242
02:28:56,928 --> 02:28:58,452
lf you arrest him.
l'll hack you.

2243
02:29:00,731 --> 02:29:01,459
l'm like wind.

2244
02:29:01,999 --> 02:29:03,694
l'll be omnipresent,
but no one can see me.

2245
02:29:04,068 --> 02:29:06,798
Neither you can see me
nor catch me,

2246
02:29:15,346 --> 02:29:17,644
Hey, Saamy's wife...
- Yes...yes.

2247
02:29:18,182 --> 02:29:18,807
Come quickly.

2248
02:29:48,879 --> 02:29:49,573
Hey, come on boys.

2249
02:29:56,554 --> 02:30:00,012
He has accounted for all the money he
received from you. lncluding interest.

2250
02:30:00,391 --> 02:30:01,517
We can't take any action against him.

2251
02:30:01,892 --> 02:30:02,824
lf possible try to escape.

2252
02:30:03,094 --> 02:30:03,685
Don't disturb us.

2253
02:30:18,743 --> 02:30:20,870
Sir, l'm Annamalai from
Madurai Highway. - Tell me.

2254
02:30:21,078 --> 02:30:22,204
Annachi's car is coming here.

2255
02:30:22,913 --> 02:30:23,538
Don't arrest him.

2256
02:30:26,083 --> 02:30:26,879
But don't allow him to
leave the district.

2257
02:30:28,753 --> 02:30:30,550
Hey turn the car...turn it.

2258
02:30:33,491 --> 02:30:34,890
Good morning sir. - Okay Babu.

2259
02:30:35,092 --> 02:30:36,719
Though you've arrest warrant
against Perumal Pitchai,

2260
02:30:36,927 --> 02:30:37,825
Why didn't you arrest him till now?

2261
02:30:38,029 --> 02:30:39,257
Can you arrest him or not?

2262
02:30:39,597 --> 02:30:40,256
What're we supposed to report?

2263
02:30:40,598 --> 02:30:41,724
Tirunelveli is eagerly waiting.

2264
02:30:42,199 --> 02:30:43,564
We must take out today's evening
paper with this news.

2265
02:30:43,768 --> 02:30:44,234
What shall we publish?

2266
02:30:44,502 --> 02:30:46,470
Publish, ''Perumal Pitchai is absconding,
police are on his trail.''

2267
02:30:46,670 --> 02:30:47,637
Then, can't you catch him?

2268
02:30:49,940 --> 02:30:50,599
''Malai Murasu''

2269
02:30:54,645 --> 02:30:56,909
PERUMAL PlTCHAl lS ABSCONDlNG.

2270
02:30:59,283 --> 02:31:01,251
Sir, post mortem is over.
We can take the body.

2271
02:31:04,121 --> 02:31:06,089
l'll light his pyre only after
arresting Perumal Pitchai.

2272
02:31:07,792 --> 02:31:08,656
Till then, let it be here.

2273
02:31:15,466 --> 02:31:16,330
This is government pistol.

2274
02:31:16,634 --> 02:31:18,602
lf there's any trouble, use it.
l'll say that l fired. - For you?

2275
02:31:19,136 --> 02:31:20,933
l've...an illegal pistol.

2276
02:31:21,372 --> 02:31:23,499
Paramasivam, stay here.

2277
02:31:34,218 --> 02:31:36,049
Sir, Annachi has changed his car.

2278
02:31:36,654 --> 02:31:37,211
l'll take care.

2279
02:31:57,842 --> 02:31:59,810
Sir, l'm Babu from Tuticorin Road.
- Tell me.

2280
02:32:00,010 --> 02:32:02,308
As suggested by you, l've diverted
Annachi on the other route.

2281
02:32:07,184 --> 02:32:10,483
Annachi, DC is waiting there with
firing orders. Please, go back.

2282
02:32:11,689 --> 02:32:12,815
Turn back.

2283
02:32:14,024 --> 02:32:14,683
Go quickly.

2284
02:32:15,025 --> 02:32:16,788
Tell me. - l've forced Annachi's
car to turn back.

2285
02:32:17,027 --> 02:32:18,654
l can't go out of
Tirunelveli district.

2286
02:32:19,029 --> 02:32:20,291
l'll go to my sand quarry.

2287
02:32:20,698 --> 02:32:22,165
You go underground.
- Okay, brother.

2288
02:32:23,434 --> 02:32:25,493
Sir, his car is entering sand quarry.

2289
02:32:26,070 --> 02:32:26,661
Okay, l'll take care.

2290
02:36:19,269 --> 02:36:22,898
Come man...come.
Arrest me...arrest me.

2291
02:36:23,640 --> 02:36:26,404
lf you arrest, you'll vanish without a trace.

2292
02:36:26,944 --> 02:36:28,935
Entire Tirunelveli will burn.

2293
02:36:30,180 --> 02:36:33,741
lf l'm in trouble, C.M. will
make a call, the next moment.

2294
02:36:34,284 --> 02:36:36,377
Next moment l'll be out.

2295
02:36:36,954 --> 02:36:38,080
lf l come out...

2296
02:36:38,455 --> 02:36:42,152
Not only in Palani, let your family
be anywhere in this world.

2297
02:36:42,459 --> 02:36:44,086
l'll exterminate your entire clan.

2298
02:36:44,461 --> 02:36:45,428
l'll not spare anyone.

2299
02:36:46,463 --> 02:36:48,931
You're safe till l'm not arrested.

2300
02:36:49,299 --> 02:36:52,325
lf you're bent upon arresting me...
Then, go ahead. Arrest me.

2301
02:36:52,803 --> 02:36:54,270
Who said l'm going to arrest you?

2302
02:36:55,305 --> 02:36:57,796
Tirunelveli will go up in flames.
l'll get a call from CM.

2303
02:36:58,642 --> 02:37:00,109
Poor innocent public
will be affected.

2304
02:37:01,945 --> 02:37:03,105
You'll exterminate my entire clan.

2305
02:37:03,547 --> 02:37:04,275
Do l need all this?

2306
02:37:04,815 --> 02:37:06,339
You said you read 20 papers everyday.

2307
02:37:07,284 --> 02:37:08,114
Did you see today's paper?

2308
02:37:09,386 --> 02:37:12,480
''Perumal Pitchai is Absconding.
Police are on his trail''

2309
02:37:13,657 --> 02:37:16,956
Why should l be afraid of you & run?
lf you've guts, arrest me.

2310
02:37:17,327 --> 02:37:19,795
Arrest me, l say.

2311
02:37:19,997 --> 02:37:22,124
lf l arrest you, it'll be
a problem for people.

2312
02:37:23,267 --> 02:37:24,791
lf you're killed, they'll make you
a patriot & put up your statue.

2313
02:37:25,169 --> 02:37:26,898
And scores of Perumal Pitchais
will generate from under it.

2314
02:37:28,172 --> 02:37:31,107
Tirunelveli would be agog
with your absconding news.

2315
02:37:32,743 --> 02:37:34,472
Let you be an absconder
all your life.

2316
02:37:35,412 --> 02:37:37,744
Let police hunt you eternally.

2317
02:37:38,849 --> 02:37:39,816
But, you'll never be found.

2318
02:37:43,187 --> 02:37:46,987
lt must be recorded that you
got scared of me & absconded.

2319
02:37:48,192 --> 02:37:49,819
Do legally whatever
you want to do.

2320
02:37:50,727 --> 02:37:51,989
You can only destroy.

2321
02:37:53,197 --> 02:37:54,323
l can create.

2322
02:37:55,332 --> 02:37:56,162
l can protect.

2323
02:38:01,705 --> 02:38:02,603
And l can destroy too.

2324
02:38:55,759 --> 02:38:58,227
Saamy's hunt will go on....

